var book = {
	"name": "1 Samuel",
	"numChapters": 31,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la don uwei u briew uba na Ramathaim-Sophim, na ka ri lum Ephraim, uba kyrteng “u Elkanah”, u khun u Jeroham, u khun u Elihu, u khun u Tohu, u khun u Suph, u nong Ephraim:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la don ar ngut ki tnga; ka kyrteng kawei “ka Hannah”, bad ka kyrteng kata kawei “ka Peninnah”: te ka Peninnah ka la don khun, hynrei, ka Hannah kam shym la don khun.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te une u briew, man ka snem u la ju leit kiew na la ka shnong sha Sheiloh ban mane bad ban kñia ha U Trai ki paid. Te ki ar ngut ki khun u Eli, u Hophni bad u Phinehas keiñ, ki lyngdoh jong U Trai, ki la don hangta.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba la poi ka sngi ba u Elkanah u la ainguh, u la ju ai ki bynta ha ka Peninnah, ka tnga jong u, bad ha ki khun shynrang jong ka bad ha ki khun kynthei jong ka baroh:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> hynrei, ha ka Hannah u la ju ai ka bynta kaba ar shah: naba u la ieit ïa ka Hannah, hynrei, U Trai u la pynlyngki ïa ka.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ka nongïaleh pyrshah jong ka, ka la pynkhih bitar khait ïa ka, khnang ban pynkhuslai ïa ka, naba U Trai u la pynlyngki ïa ka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad namar ba u la ju leh kumta man ka snem, haba ka la leit kiew ha ïing U Trai, ka ruh ka la ju pynkhih bitar ïa ka; haduh ba ka ju ïam, ka jingbam ruh kam ju bam.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Elkanah u tnga jong ka u la ong ha ka, “Ko Hannah, balei pha ïam? balei ruh pham bam jingbam? balei pha khuslai ruh ha la ka dohnud? nga ngam long kham bha ïa pha ban ïa shiphew ngut ki khun shynrang?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta, ynda ki la bam la dih ha Sheiloh, ka Hannah ka la ïeng. Te u Eli lyngdoh u shong ha la ka jingshong hajan u rishot ka jingkhang ka templ U Trai.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ka la kthang ka mynsiem jong ka, ka la duwai ruh ha U Trai, ka da ïam eh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka la smai da ka kular ruh, ka da ong, “A Trai ki paid, lada shisha men khmih ïa ka jingjynjar ka shakri jong me, bad men kynmaw ïa nga, men ym klet ruh ïa la ka shakri, hynrei, men da ai khun shynrang ha la ka shakri, te nga ruh ngan aiti ïa u ha U Trai baroh ki sngi ka rta jong u, bad ka syrti kan ym dei ïa ka khlieh jong u.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te katba ka ïaiduwai ha khmat U Trai, u Eli u la khmih ïa ka shyntur jong ka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ka Hannah, ka la kren ha la ka dohnud; hynrei, tang ki rmiang shyntur jong ka ki la khih, ïa ka ktien jong ka te ym ïohsngew: namar kata, u Eli u la tharai ba ka la buaid.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Eli u la ong ruh ha ka, “Sa katno phan long kaba buaid? to da buh noh ïa kata ka Waiñ jong pha.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ka Hannah ka la ïathuh ka la ong ruh, “Em, ko kynrad, hynrei, nga ka briew ka bajynjar ka mynsiem: ïa ka Waiñ lane ka kyiad ngam shym la dih, hynrei, nga la theh noh ïa la ka mynsiem ha khmat U Trai.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Wat ñiew ka khun u Belial ïa la ka shakri: naba na kaba dap tam ka jingshitom jong nga bad ka jingpynbitar ïa nga, nga la kren baroh shi katta.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Eli u la ïathuh, u la ong ruh, “To khie leit ha kaba suk: U Blei ki Israel un ai ruh ïa kata ka jingkyrpad kaba pha la kyrpad na u.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ka te ka la ong, “Ai ba ka shakri jong me kan shem ka jingisynei ha khmat jong me.” Kumta, kata ka kynthei ka la leit noh, ka la bam ruh, bad kam shym leh sa shuh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ki la khie la dang step, bad ki la ïamane ha khmat U Trai, ki la leit wan noh ruh, bad ki la poi ha la ïing ha Ramah: bad u Elkanah u la ithuh ïa ka Hannah ka tnga jong u; bad U Trai u la kynmaw ïa ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ynda ka Hannah ka la punkhun, haba ka la dap bnai, ka la kha khun shynrang; bad ka la kyrteng ïa u, “u Samuel”, ka da ong, “Naba na U Trai nga la pan ïa u.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad uta u briew, u Elkanah lem bad ka ïing jong u baroh, ki la leit kiew ïa ka ban ainguh ha U Trai ïa ka jingkñia ba shi sien shi snem, bad ïa ka jingkular jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, ka Hannah kam shym leit; naba ka la ong ha la u tnga, “Ngan ym leit kiew, tad ynda la pyniehnoh buiñ ïa u khynnah, hadien te ngan ïalam bad ïa u ruh, ba un paw ha khmat U Trai, ba un ïaisah ruh hangta junom.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Elkanah u tnga jong ka u la ong ha ka, “Leh katba pha ibit; nang shong ha ban da pha la pyniehnoh buiñ ïa u; tang ba U Trai un pyndep ïa ka ktien jong u.” Kumta, kata ka kynthei ka la shong bad ka la ri ïa u khynnah, tad ynda ka la pyniehnoh buiñ ïa u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba ka la pyniehnoh buiñ ïa u, ka la leit lam ïa u lem bad ka, bad lai tylli ki masi dab, bad shi ephah u 'purew, bad shi lywa ka Waiñ, bad ka la ïalam ïa u sha kata ka ïing U Trai ha Sheiloh: te u khynnah u dang khynnah eh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ki la pynïap ïa u masi, bad ki la ïalam ïa u khynnah ha u Eli.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te ka la ong, “Ko kynrad, katba ka im ka mynsiem jong me, ko kynrad, nga long kata ka briew kaba la ïeng hangne hajan jong me, nga da duwai ha U Trai.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar une u khynnah nga la duwai; te U Trai u la ai ha nga ïa kata ka jingkyrpad kaba nga la pan na u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Namar kata, nga ruh nga la ai noh ïa u ha U Trai; baroh ki sngi ka rta jong u, la ai noh ïa u ha U Trai.” Bad u la mane ïa U Trai hangta."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka Hannah ka la duwai, bad ka la ong: “Ka dohnud jong nga ka leh kmen ha U Trai, ïa ka reng jong nga la pynkyntiew ha U Trai; la plie wang ïa ka shyntur jong nga halor ki nongshun jong nga: namar nga leh kmen ha ka jingpynim jong me.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Ym don u bakhuid kat U Trai; naba nalor jong me ym don shuh mano mano; lymne ym don u mawsiang kum U Blei jong ngi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Wat da kren sarong eh shuh; wat ai ban mih ka jingmeng na ka shyntur jong phi: namar U Trai u long U Blei ka jingtip, bad u ju thew ïa ki jingleh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ïa ki ryntieh jong ki bakhlaiñ la pynkheiñ, bad ïa ki batlot bor la panpoh da ka bor.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kita kiba la ju dap kyrhai ki la tyrwa nong ïa lade ban ïoh kpu: bad kita kiba ju thngan kim long kumta shuh: kumta, kaba lyngki ka la kha hynñiew ngut; bad kata kaba bun ki khun ka nangswai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U Trai uba pynïap, bad uba pynim: u pynhiar ma u sha ka jingtep, u pynmih ruh ma u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U Trai uba pynshipa, bad uba pynriewspah: ma u, uba pyndem, bad uba pynkyntiew.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U pynïeng ïa ki baduk na ka 'dewmet, u pynkyntiew ruh ïa ki bakyrduh khait na ka thliew sboh, ban pynshong ïa ki lem bad ki syiem, bad ban pynïoh ha ki ka khet ka burom; naba ki rijied jong ka khyndew ki long ki jong U Trai, bad u la pynshong ma u ïa ka pyrthei halor jong ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Un sumar ïa ki sla'jat ki riewkhuid jong u, hynrei, ïa u bymman un pynsngap noh jar ha ka jingdum; namar un ym jop uno uno u briew da ka bor.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Yn pynlwet jin ïa ki nongïaleh pyrshah ïa U Trai; na bneng un tied pyrthat pyrshah ïa ki: U Trai un bishar ïa ka bakut ka pyrthei; un ai bor ruh ha la u syiem, bad un pynkyntiew ïa ka reng jong uba la sleh jong u.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Elkanah u la leit sha Ramah ha la ïing. Te uta u khun khynnah u la shakri ïa U Trai ha khmat u Eli lyngdoh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki khun u Eli ki la long ki khun u Belial; kim ithuh ïa U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ka rukom ki lyngdoh bad ki briew ka la long, ba haba uno uno u la ainguh ka jingkñia, u shakri u lyngdoh u ju wan haba dang shet ïa ka doh, bad u proh u balai pnat ha la ka kti;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> te u la ju dung ïa u ha ka nar sdieh, lane ha u khiew rnong, lane ha u dek, lane ha u khiew phiang; baroh katba ngat ha u proh, u lyngdoh u la ju shim ha lade. Kumta, ki la ju leh ha Sheiloh ha ki Israel baroh kiba la wan shata.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad haba ym pat thang ïa ka khleiñ ruh, u shakri u lyngdoh u ju wan, u da ong ruh ha u briew uba kñia, “To ai doh ban syang ïa u lyngdoh; naba un ym shim ïa ka doh kaba la shet, hynrei, kaba im.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad lada, uno uno ruh u briew u ong ha u, “Hynrei, kin da thang shuwa ïa ka khleiñ, hadien te men shim katba mon ka mynsiem jong me;” u te un da ong, “Em, hynrei men ai mynta keiñ; lym kumta, ngan shim ïa ka da ka bor.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta, ka pop jong kita ki samla ka la khraw eh ha khmat U Trai; naba ki briew ki la isih ïa ka jingainguh jong U Trai.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Samuel u la shakri ha khmat U Trai, u dang khynnah, ba la panpoh ïa u da ka ephod linen.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka kmie jong u ruh ka ju thaw sopti ka barit ïa u, ka la ju wallam ruh ïa ka man la ka snem, haba ka la wan kiew lem bad u tnga jong ka ban ainguh ïa ka jingkñia ba shi snem.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Eli u la kyrkhu ïa u Elkanah bad ïa ka tnga jong u, bad u la ong, “To U Trai un ai symbai ha me na kane ka briew namar kata ka jingai kylliang kaba la ai kylliang ha U Trai.” Te ki la leit wan noh sha la ïing.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad U Trai u la wan khmih ïa ka Hannah, bad ka la punkhun, ka la kha ruh lai ngut ki shynrang bad ar ngut ki kynthei. Bad uta u khynnah, u Samuel u la nang san ha khmat U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Eli u la tymmen eh; bad u la ïohsngew baroh ba ki khun jong u ki la leh ha ki Israel baroh, kumno ba ki la ju thiah ruh bad kita ki kynthei kiba ju shakri ha ka jingkhang Ka Tabernakl ka jingïaseng.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “Balei phi leh kiba kum kine? Naba nga ïohsngew ïa ki jingleh basniew jong phi na kine ki briew baroh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Em phi, ko khun; naba kane ka jingbna ba nga ïohsngew kam long ka babha; phi pynleh ïa ki briew jong U Trai ban leh palat.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Lada u briew un leh pop ïa u parabriew, U Blei un bishar ïa u; hynrei, lada u briew un leh pop ïa U Trai, uei u ban ïasaid na ka bynta jong u?” Pynban, kim shym sngap ïa ka ktien u kpa jong ki, naba U Trai u la thew ban pynïap noh ïa ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te uta u khynnah u Samuel u la nang san, bad u la long uba sngewbha ïa u da U Trai, bad da ki briew de.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te uwei u briew u jong U Blei u la wan ha u Eli, bad u la ong ha u, “Kumne u ong U Trai, ‘Nga ngam shym la paw shynna ha ka ïing u kpa jong me, mynba ki dang don ha Ijipt ha ka ïing u Pharaoh?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Nga ngam shym la jied ïa u ruh na ki jaid Israel baroh ban long u lyngdoh jong nga, ban leit kiew ha ka duwan jong nga, ban thang ka jingiwbih, bad ban phong ïa ka ephod ha khmat jong nga? ngam shym la aiti ruh ha ka ïing u kpa jong me ïa ki jingainguh baroh kiba da ka ding ki jong ki khun Israel?",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Balei te phi ïuhbeiñ ïa ka jingkñia jong nga bad ïa ka jingainguh jong nga, kiba nga la hukum ban long ha ka jaka shong jong nga: ba me kham pyndonburom ruh ïa la ki khun ban ïa nga, phi da pynsngaid ïa lade da kita ki jingainguh baroh ki babha tam ki jong ki briew jong nga ki Israel?’",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Namar kata, U Trai, uba U Blei ki Israel, u ong, ‘Nga la ong shisha ba ka ïing jong me, bad ka ïing u kpa jong me, kin ïaid ha khmat jong nga junom:’ hynrei, mynta U Trai u ong, ‘Kata kaba eh ïa nga; naba kiba pyndonburom ïa nga, ïa kita nga ruh ngan pyndonburom, te ïa kita kiba ñiewbeiñ ïa nga, yn ñiewbeiñ kylliang ïa ki.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ha khmih, ki sngi kin wan, ha kiba ngan ot noh ïa ka ksang'ti jong me, bad ïa ka ksang'ti ka ïing u kpa jong me, ba yn ym don u riewtymmen ha ka ïing jong me.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad men ïohi ïa ka jingjynjar ka jaka shong jong nga, ha ka jingmanbha baroh ïa kaba U Blei un ai ha Israel; bad yn ym don riewtymmen ha ïing jong me junom.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad uta u briew jong me, ïa uba ngan ym ot noh na ka duwan jong nga, un sah ba un bam duh ïa ki khmat jong me, bad ba un pynjynjar ïa ka dohnud jong me: bad ka jingroi ka ïing jong me baroh kin ïap ruh ha kaba dang shiteng met.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te kane kan long ka dak ha me, ka ban hap halor ki ar ngut ki khun shynrang jong me, halor u Hophni bad u Phinehas; ha kajuh ka sngi kin ïap noh baroh ar ngut.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad ngan pynmih ha lade ïa u lyngdoh uba ngeit, u ban leh kat kaba don ha ka dohnud jong nga bad ha ka jingmut jong nga: bad ngan tei ïa ka ïing kaba skhem ha u; bad un ïaid ha khmat uba la sleh jong nga junom.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kan jia ruh, ba uwei uwei baroh ïa uba la pynsah na ka ïing jong me un wan un dem ngon ruh ha u ba un ïoh shi dkhot ka rupa bad uwei u kpu, bad un ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to thung ïa nga ha kano kano ka kam kaba dei lyngdoh, ba ngan dup ïoh bam khyndiat u kpu.” ’ ”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad uta u khynnah, u Samuel u la shakri ïa U Trai ha khmat u Eli. Bad ka ktien U Trai ka la long ka bakordor ha kita ki sngi; ym shym don ka jingithuhpaw kaba shynna.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ha kata ka por, mynba u Eli u dang thiah ha la ka jaka, haba ki khmat jong u ki la sdang ban byrïe, ba um lah ban ïohi,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad haba ym pat lip ka sharak U Blei ha ka templ U Trai, ha kaba la don ka synduk U Blei, u Samuel ruh u la thiah;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> kumta, U Trai u la khot ïa u Samuel: u ruh u la ong, “Nga hangne.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la phet sha u Eli, bad u la ong, “Nga hangne: ba me la khot ïa nga.” U te u la ong, “Ngam shym khot; leit thiah pat.” Bad u la leit bad u la thiah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Trai u la nang khot ïa u pat, “Samuel.” Bad u Samuel u la khie bad u la leit sha u Eli, bad u la ong, “Nga hangne; ba me la khot ïa nga.” U te u la ong, “Ngam shym khot, ko khun; leit thiah pat.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Samuel um pat shym la ithuh ïa U Trai, lymne ym pat shym la pynpaw ha u ïa ka ktien U Trai.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad U Trai u la khot pat ïa u Samuel ka balai sien. Bad u la khie bad u la leit sha u Eli, bad u la ong, “Nga hangne; ba me la khot ïa nga.” Te u Eli u la tip ba dei U Trai uba la khot ïa u khynnah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Namar kata, u Eli u la ong ha u Samuel, “Khie leit thiah: te lada un khot ïa me, to ong, ‘Kren, ko Trai; naba u shakri jong me u ïohsngew.’ ” Kumta, u Samuel u la leit bad u la thiah ha la ka jaka.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad U Trai u la wan, bad U la ïeng, bad U la khot kumba mynshuwa, “Samuel, Samuel.” Te u Samuel u la ong, “To kren; naba u shakri jong me u ïohsngew.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u Samuel, “Ha khmih, ngan sa leh ei ei ha Israel, ha kaba uno uno baroh haba un ïohsngew ïa ka, kin kyllut noh ngiang ki shkor jong u baroh ar.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ha kata ka sngi ngan pyndep noh halor u Eli ïa kita kiei kiei baroh kiba nga la kren shaphang ka ïing jong u, naduh kaba sdang haduh ka bakut.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Namar nga la ong ha u hi ba ngan bishar pynrem junom ïa ka ïing jong u, namar kata ka jingbymman kaba u tip ma u, naba ki khun jong u ki la pynlong ka jingtim ïa lade, u te um shym la khang ïa ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Namar kata, nga la smai ha ka ïing u Eli, ba yn ym sait ïa ka jingbymman ka ïing u Eli da ka jingkñia lymne da ka jingainguh junom.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Samuel u la thiah haduh mynstep, bad u la plie ïa ki jingkhang ka ïing U Trai. U Samuel te u la sheptieng ban ïathuh ïa kata ka jingithuhpaw ha u Eli.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Eli u la khot ïa u Samuel, bad u la ong, “Ko Samuel, u khun jong nga,” u ruh u la ong, “Nga hangne.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la ong, “Kaei kata kaba U Trai u la kren ha me? Nga kyrpad ïa me wat buhrieh ïa ka na nga: U Blei un leh kumne ïa me, bad tam ruh, lada men buhrieh ei ei na nga na kita kiei kiei baroh kiba u la kren ha me.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Samuel u la ïathuh ha u ïa kiei kiei baroh, bad um shym la buhrieh ei ei ruh na u. U te u la ong, “U long U Trai; to un leh ïa kaba u hi u sngewbha.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Samuel u la nang roi, bad U Trai u la don lem bad u, bad um shym shah ïa kawei na ki ktien jong u ban hap duh noh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ki Israel baroh naduh Dan haduh Beer-sheba ki la tip ba la pynskhem ïa u Samuel ban long u nongïathuhlypa jong U Trai.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad U Trai u la paw pat ha Sheiloh: naba U Trai u la pynpaw ïa lade ïa u Samuel ha Sheiloh da ka ktien U Trai."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad ka ktien u Samuel ka la wan ha ki Israel baroh. Te ki Israel ki la leit ïaleh thma ïa ki Philistia, bad ki la sher dara hajan ka Ebeneser: ki Philistia ruh ki la sher dara ha Aphek.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la khreh riang ïa lade pyrshah ïa ki Israel: te haba ki la ïaleh, la jop ïa ki Israel ha khmat ki Philistia: bad ki la pynïap noh ha madan kumba saw hajar ki briew na ki paidïapom.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ynda kita ki paidbah ki la ïawan sha ka jaka shong dara, ki tymmen basan jong ki Israel ki la ïa-ong, “Balei U Trai u la shoh ïa ngi mynta ha khmat ki Philistia? Ïa ngin ïaleit shim sha ngi na Sheiloh ïa ka synduk ka jutang U Trai, ba kan wan hapdeng jong ngi, ïa ka ban pynim ïa ngi na ka kti ki nongshun jong ngi.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Kumta, u paidbah u la phah sha Sheiloh, bad ki la wallam nangta ïa kata ka synduk ka jutang jong U Trai ki paid, uba shong hapdeng kita ki Kherub: te ki khun u Eli ar ngut, u Hophni bad u Phinehas keiñ, ki la don lem hangta bad ka synduk ka jutang U Blei.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba ka la wan ka synduk ka jutang U Trai sha ka jaka shong dara, ki Israel baroh ki la risa da ka jingrisa kaba jam, katba ka la sawa pat ka khyndew.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew ki Philistia ïa ka jingsawa kata ka jingrisa ki la ïa-ong, “Kaei kane ka jingsawa ka jingrisa kaba jam katne ha ka jaka shong dara kine ki Hebru?” Bad ki la tip ba ka synduk U Trai ka la wan poi sha ka jaka shong dara.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la sheptieng, naba ki la ong, “U Blei u la wan poi sha kata ka jaka shong dara.” Ki la ong ruh, “Kordit ïa ngi! namar ym shym jia mynno mynno ruh kaba kum kane.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kordit ïa ngi! uei u ban pynim ïa ngi na ka kti jong kine ki blei kiba don bor? Dei kine ki blei kiba la shoh ïa ki Ijipt da kita ki jingïapthem baroh ha kata ka ri khlaw.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> To pynïaw phi ïa lade, to long rangbah, ko phi ki Philistia, ïoh phin long shakri ïa kine ki Hebru, kumba ma ki, ki la shakri ïa phi: to long rangbah phi, to ïaleh ruh.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki Philistia ki la ïaleh, bad la jop noh ïa ki Israel, bad ki la phet ïap noh uwei uwei baroh sha la ka ïingjaiñ: te ka la long ka jingpynïap kaba khraw eh; naba la kyllon na ki Israel laiphew hajar ki shipai ba ïaleh na tbian.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad la knieh ïa ka synduk U Blei ruh; bad ïa kita ki ar ngut ki khun u Eli, u Hophni bad u Phinehas, la pynïap noh de.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te uwei u briew na ki Benjamin u la phet na uta u paidïapom, bad u la poi sha Sheiloh ha kata ka sngi, uba ki jaiñ jong u la pynkad, bad uba la sum khyndew ha ka khlieh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad haba u la poi, ha khmih, u Eli u shong ha ka jingshong harud lynti ba u da ap khnang: namar ka dohnud jong u ka la syier shaphang ka synduk U Blei. Te haba uta u briew u la poi sha shnong, bad ba u la pynbna ïa kata, ka shnong baroh ka la lynñiar.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u Eli u la ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa kata ka jinglynñiar, u la ong, “Kaei kane ka jingsawa kane ka jingkhihwin?” Te uta u briew u la wan kyrkieh bad u la ïathuh ha u Eli.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Eli u la khyndaiphew phra snem ka rta; bad ki khmat jong u ki la byrïe, ba um lah ïohi shuh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad uta u briew u la ong ha u Eli, “Nga long uta uba la wan na u paidïapom, bad ha kane ka sngi nga la wan phet na uta u paidïapom.” U te u la ong, “Kumno ka la long, ko khun?”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad uta uba la wallam khubor u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Ki Israel ki la phet ïap ha khmat ki Philistia, bad ka la long ka jingpynïap kaba khraw ruh hapdeng u paidbah, ki khun jong me ruh baroh ar ngut, u Hophni bad u Phinehas, ki la ïap, bad ki la knieh ruh ïa ka synduk U Blei.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba u la ïathuh shaphang ka synduk U Blei, u la kyllon lyndang na kata ka jingshong hajan ka khyrdop, bad la kheiñ ka ryndang jong u, bad u la ïap: naba u la long u briew uba la tymmen, bad uba khia. Te u la lah bishar ïa ki Israel sawphew snem.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka pyrsa kurim jong u, ka tnga u Phinehas, kaba la punkhun, bad ka la jan kha ruh; te haba ka la ïohsngew ïa kita ki jingbna ba la knieh ïa ka synduk U Blei, bad ba la ïap u kthaw kurim bad u tnga jong ka, ka la dem ïa lade bad ka la kha; naba ki jingsuh khun jong ka ki la jia ha ka.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te hamar ka por ba kan sa ïap, kita ki kynthei kiba la don lem bad ka ki la ïa-ong, “Wat sheptieng; naba pha la kha khun shynrang.” Hynrei, ka kam shym phai ktien, kam shym sngew ruh ïa kata.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ka la kyrteng ïa u khynnah “u Ikhabod”, da kaba ong, “Kata ka burom ka la jah noh na Israel”: namar ba la knieh ïa ka synduk U Blei, bad namar uta u kthaw kurim jong ka bad u tnga jong ka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ka la ong, “Kata ka burom ka la jah noh na Israel; namar ba la knieh ïa ka synduk U Blei.”"
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la shim ïa ka synduk U Blei na Ebeneser, bad ki la leit lam noh ïa ka sha Ashdod.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki Philistia, haba ki la shim ïa ka synduk U Blei, ki la wallam ïa ka hapoh ka ïing u Dagon, bad ki la buh ïa ka hajan u Dagon.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki Ashdod ha kaba lashai ki la khie dang step, te ha khmih, u Dagon u la kyllon da pyrkup ha ka khyndew ha khmat kata ka synduk U Trai. Te ki la shim ïa u Dagon, bad ki la pynïeng pat ïa u ha la ka jaka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ha kaba lashai pat ki la khie la dang step, te ha khmih, u Dagon u la kyllon da pyrkup ha ka khyndew ha khmat kata ka synduk U Trai; bad ka khlieh u Dagon bad baroh ar ki slakti jong u ki la don ha ka jingryngkang, ba ki la lah dkut noh; ka la sah sa tang ka met hi ha u Dagon.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar kata, kita ki lyngdoh u Dagon, lymne kita kiba ju leit ha ïing u Dagon, kim ïuh ïa ka jingryngkang u Dagon ha Ashdod, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ka kti U Trai ka la ban khia halor ki Ashdod, bad u la pynjot ïa ki bad u la pynngat ïa ka jingpang ba lang snam ha ki, ha Ashdod ruh bad ha ki phang jong ka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba ki Ashdod ki la ïohi ba ka la long kumta, ki la ïa-ong, “Kane ka synduk U Blei ki Israel kan ym ïoh sah bad ngi: naba ka kti jong u ka pynshitom eh halor jong ngi, bad halor u blei jong ngi u Dagon.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Namar kata, ki la phah ïalum lang sha ki, ïa ki doloi ki Philistia baroh, bad ki la ïa-ong, “Ngin leh kumno ïa kane ka synduk U Blei ki Israel?” Ki te ki la ong, “Ai ba yn bah noh ïa kata ka synduk U Blei ki Israel sha Gath.” Te ki la ïabah noh ïa ka synduk U Blei ki Israel shata.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ynda ki la bah noh ïa ka, ka kti U Trai ka la ïaleh pyrshah ïa kata ka shnong ruh da ka jingpynjot kaba khraw eh: bad u la pynshitom ïa ki rangbah jong kata ka shnong, ki barit bad ki bakhraw, bad ka jingpang ba lang snam ka la mih ha ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, ki la phah lam noh ïa ka synduk U Blei sha Ekron. Te haba ka synduk U Blei ka la poi ha Ekron, ki Ekron ki la lynñiar, ki la ong, “Ki la wallam ïa kane ka synduk U Blei ki Israel ha ngi, ïa ka ban pynïap ïa ngi bad ïa ki briew jong ngi.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta te, ki la phah ïalum lang ïa ki doloi ki Philistia baroh, bad ki la ïa-ong, “To phah noh ïa kane ka synduk U Blei ki Israel, to ai ruh ba kan leit noh pat ha ka jaka jong ka, ba kan ym pynïap ïa ngi, bad ïa ki briew jong ngi:” naba ka la don ka jingpynjot kaba pynïap ha kata ka shnong baroh; ka kti U Blei ka la ban khia eh hangta.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad kita ki briew ki bym shym la ïap ki la ngat kata ka jingpang ba lang snam: bad ka jinglynñiar ka shnong ka la leit kiew sha bneng."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ka synduk U Trai ka la sah ha ka ri ki Philistia hynñiew bnai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki Philistia ki la phah khot ïa ki lyngdoh bad ïa ki nongkhan, ki da ong, “Ngin leh kumno ïa kane ka synduk U Trai? to ïathuh ha ngi da kumno ngin phah noh ïa ka sha ka jaka jong ka.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki te ki la ong, “Lada phin phah noh ïa ka synduk U Blei ki Israel, wat phah noh suda ïa ka; hynrei, la kumno kumno phin ai ha u ïa ka jingainguh namar ka jingpalat: te kumta yn pynkhiah ïa phi, bad phin ïoh tip namar balei ba ka kti jong u kam pat kynriah na phi.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki ruh ki la ïa-ong, “Kaei kata ka jingainguh namar ka jingpalat kaba ngin ai ha u?” Te ki la ïathuh, “San tylli ki dur ki jingat lang snam da ka ksiar, bad san tylli ki khnai ksiar, katba kum ka jingkheiñ ki doloi ki Philistia: naba ha phi baroh bad ha ki doloi jong phi, ka la ngat kajuh ka jingpang.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar kata, phin thaw keiñ ïa ki dur jong kita ki jingat lang snam jong phi, bad ïa ki dur jong kita ki khnai jong phi kiba pynjot noh ïa ka khyndew; to ai burom ruh ha U Blei ki Israel: lehse un pynsting ïa la ka kti na phi, bad na kine ki blei jong phi, bad na ka khyndew jong phi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te balei phi pyneh ïa la ki dohnud, kumba ki Ijipt bad u Pharaoh ki la ïa-pyneh ïa ki dohnud jong ki? haba u la leh ïa kaba phylla hapdeng jong ki, ki kim shym la pyllait noh ïa ki paidbah, ki ruh ki la leit noh?",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mynta te, to phin thaw ïa ka kali ka bathymmai, to shim ruh ar tylli ki masi ai dud, ha kiba ym shym la buh ïa ka lyngkor, to teh ruh ïa kita ki masi ha kata ka kali bad to wallam noh ïa ki khun masi na ki sha ïing;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> phin shim ruh ïa ka synduk U Trai, bad phin buh ïa ka halor kata ka kali; te kita ki mar ksiar kiba phi la ai ha u ban long ka jingainguh namar ka jingpalat, phin thep hapoh i synduk bad buh ha krung jong ka; bad to phah noh ïa ka, ba kan leit noh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Phin khmih ruh, lada ka leit kiew na kata ka lynti ka phang jong ka hi sha Beth-shemesh, te kumta u la pynngat ma u ïa kane ka jingsniew ka bakhraw halor jong ngi: hynrei, lada em, ngin ïoh tip ba ym dei ka kti jong u ba la shoh ïa ngi; kane ka la shu jia ryngkhat ha ngi.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kita ki rangbah ki la leh kumta; bad ki la shim ar tylli ki masi ai dud, bad ki la teh ïa ki ha kata ka kali, bad ki la set hapoh ïing ïa ki khun jong ki:",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> bad ki la buh ïa ka synduk U Trai halor kata ka kali, bad ita i synduk ruh ba la buh kita ki khnai ksiar bad kita ki dur ki jingat lang snam jong ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad kita ki masi ki la leit na kaba beit ka lynti sha ka lynti Beth-shemesh; na ka lynti bah keiñ ki la leit, ki da pah keiñ katba ki dang leit, bad kim shym la phai noh sha kamon lymne sha kadiang; kita ki doloi jong ki Philistia ki la bud nadien jong ki haduh ka pud Beth-shemesh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ki Beth-shemesh ki dang ïa-ot ïa u Kew jong ki ha ka them: bad ki la khmied ïa la ki khmat, bad ki la ïohi ïa kata ka synduk, te ki la kmen haba ki la ïohi ïa ka.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te kata ka kali ka la poi sha ka lyngkha u Joshua u nong Beth-shemesh, bad ka la sangeh hangta, ha kaba la don u maw uba heh: ki te ki la thlieh ïa ki dieng jong kata ka kali, bad ki la kñia ainguh ïa kita ki masi ban long ka jingainguh thang ha U Trai.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki Lebi ki la pynhiar ïa ka synduk U Trai, bad ïa ita i synduk iba bad ka, ha iba ki la don kita ki mar ksiar, bad ki la buh ïa ki halor uta u mawbah: bad ki Beth-shemesh ki la ainguh ïa ki jingainguh thang bad ki la kñia ki jingkñia ha U Trai ha kata ka sngi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba kita ki san ngut ki doloi ki Philistia ki la ïohi ïa kata, ki la leit wan noh sha Ekron ha kata ka sngi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad kita ki dur ki jingat lang snam da ka ksiar kiba ki Philistia ki la ai ban long ka jingainguh namar ka jingpalat ha U Trai ki long kine; namar ka Ashdod kawei, namar ka Gasa kawei, namar ka Ashkelon kawei, namar ka Gath kawei, namar ka Ekron kawei;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad kita ki khnai ksiar, katba kum ka jingkheiñ ki nongbah ki Philistia baroh kiba la dei ha kita ki san ngut ki doloi, kita ki nongbah ba la ker kynroh bad ki nongrit kiba khlem kynroh ruh: haduh uta u mawbah, ha uba ki la buh ïa ka synduk U Trai, uta u maw u dang sah haduh kane ka sngi keiñ ha ka lyngkha u Joshua u nong Beth-shemesh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te U la pynïap ïa ki rangbah Beth-shemesh, namar ba ki la jngoh hapoh ka synduk U Trai, U la pynïap keiñ na kita ki briew hynñiewphew ngut, bad sanphew hajar ki rangbah: bad kita ki briew ki la ïam, namar ba U Trai u la pynïap ïa kita ki briew da ka jingpynïap kaba khraw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad ki Beth-shemesh ki la ïa-ong, “Uei uba lah ban ïeng ha khmat une U Trai, une U Blei u bakhuid? Bad sha kino un leit noh na ngi?”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ki la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien sha ki Kiriath-jearim, ki da ong, “Ki Philistia ki la wallam noh pat ïa ka synduk U Trai; to wan hiar noh, ba phin ïalam noh artet ïa ka sha phi.”"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki rangbah Kiriath-jearim ki la wan, bad ki la wallam noh artet ïa ka synduk U Trai, bad ki la wallam ïa ka ha ka ïing u Abinadab ha uta u lum, bad ki la pynkyntang ïa u Eleasar u khun jong u ïa ka ban sumar ïa ka synduk U Trai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te naduh ba kata ka synduk ka la wan shong ha Kiriath-jearim, ka la long slem, jin arphew snem keiñ: bad ka ïing Israel baroh ka la ïam sngewkynmaw ïa U Trai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Samuel u la kren ha ka ïing Israel baroh, u da ong, “Lada phin phai noh sha U Trai da ka dohnud jong phi baroh, to bred noh ïa kita ki blei khyllah bad ïa ki Ashtaroth napdeng jong phi, bad to khreh ïa la ki dohnud sha U Trai, to shakri ruh tang ïa u hi: u te un pyllait noh ïa phi na ka kti ki Philistia.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, ki khun Israel ki la bred noh ïa ki Baal bad ïa ki Ashtaroth, bad ki la shakri tang ïa U Trai hi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ong, “To ïalum ïa ki Israel baroh sha Mispah, te ngan duwai na ka bynta jong phi ha U Trai.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki la ïalum lang ha Mispah, bad ki la ïatong um, bad ki la ïatheh ha khmat U Trai, bad ki la ïashah jingit ha kata ka sngi, bad ki la ïa-ong hangta, “Ngi la leh pop ïa U Trai.” Bad u Samuel u la bishar ïa ki khun Israel ha Mispah.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba ki Philistia ki la ïohsngew ba ki Israel ki la ïalum lang ha Mispah, kita ki doloi jong ki Philistia ki la leit kiew ïaleh ïa ki Israel. Bad haba ki khun Israel ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la sheptieng ïa ki Philistia.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ki khun Israel ki la ïa-ong ha u Samuel, “Ma me to wat shongthait ïa ka ban lynñiar kyrpad na ka bynta jong ngi ha U Trai U Blei jong ngi, ba un pyllait ïa ngi na ka kti kine ki Philistia.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Samuel u la shim ïa u khun langbrot ba dang buiñ, bad u la ainguh ïa u baroh phar ban long ka jingainguh thang ha U Trai; bad u Samuel u la lynñiar kyrpad ha U Trai na ka bynta ki Israel; bad U Trai u la shahshkor ïa u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad katba u Samuel u dang ainguh ïa kata ka jingainguh thang, ki Philistia ki la ïawan hajan ïa ka ban ïaleh ïa ki Israel: hynrei, U Trai u la tied pyrthat da ki pyrthat kiba khraw halor ki Philistia ha kata ka sngi, bad u la pynjot noh ïa ki; bad la pynïap ïa ki ha khmat ki Israel.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki rangbah Israel ki la ïamih noh na Mispah, bad ki la beh ïa ki Philistia, bad ki la pynïap ïa ki haduh ba ki la poi hapoh Beth-kar.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Samuel u la shim ïa u maw, bad u la pynïeng ïa u hapdeng ka Mispah bad ka Shen, bad u la khot kyrteng ïa u, “U Ebeneser”, u da ong, “Haduh kane U Trai u la ïarap ïa ngi.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta la jop ïa ki Philistia, bad kim shym wan shuh sha ka pud ki Israel: bad ka kti U Trai ka la long pyrshah ïa ki Philistia baroh ki sngi u Samuel.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad kita ki nongbah kiba ki Philistia ki la lah knieh na ki Israel la ai noh pat ïa ki ha ki Israel, naduh Ekron haduh Gath; bad ki Israel ki la knieh noh ruh ïa la ki pud na ka kti ki Philistia. Te la don ka jingïasuk hapdeng ki Israel bad ki Amor.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Samuel u la bishar ïa ki Israel baroh ki sngi ka rta jong u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la ju leit kylleng man la ka snem sha Bethel, sha Gilgal, bad sha Mispah; bad u la bishar ïa ki Israel ha kita ki jaka baroh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te ka jingwan phai jong u ka la long sha Ramah, namar ka ïing jong u ka la don hangta; hangta ruh u la ju bishar ïa ki Israel: bad hangta u la thaw ïa ka duwan ha U Trai."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u Samuel u la tymmen, u la thung ïa la ki khun ba kin long nongbishar halor ki Israel.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ka kyrteng u khun nyngkong jong u ka la long “u Joel”; bad ka kyrteng u ba-ar, “u Abijah”: te kine ki la long nongbishar ha Beer-sheba.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te kita ki khun jong u kim shym ïaid ha ki lynti jong u, hynrei, ki la phai noh sha ka jinglalot, bad ki la bamsap, bad ki la pynbakla ïa ka jingbishar ruh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, ki tymmen basan ki Israel baroh ki la ïalum lang, bad ki la ïawan sha u Samuel ha Ramah:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> bad ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Ha khmih, ma me, me la tymmen, bad ki khun jong me kim ïaid ha ki lynti jong me: mynta te to thung da u syiem halor jong ngi ban bishar ïa ngi kum ki jaid bynriew baroh.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te kane ka ktien ka la pynsngewsih ïa u Samuel, haba ki la ong, “To ai da u syiem ban bishar ïa ngi.” Bad u Samuel u la duwai ha U Trai.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Samuel, “To shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong kine ki briew ha kiei kiei baroh ba ki ong ha me: namar ym dei ïa me ba ki la kyntait, hynrei, ki la kyntait ïa nga, ba ngan ym long syiem shuh halor jong ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Katba kum kita ki kam baroh kiba ki la leh naduh kata ka sngi ba nga la wallam noh ïa ki na Ijipt haduh kane ka sngi, ha kaba ki la kyntait ïa nga, bad ba ki la shakri ïa kiwei pat ki blei, kumta ki leh ïa me ruh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te namar kata, to sngap ïa ka ktien jong ki: la kumta ruh da kaba phla to phla pyrshah ïa ki, bad to pyni ha ki, ïa ka rukom uta u syiem u ban synshar halor jong ki.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Samuel u la ïathuh ïa ki ktien U Trai baroh ha kita ki briew kiba pan syiem na u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u la ong, “Kane ka rukom uta u syiem u ban synshar halor jong phi: un shim na ki khun shynrang jong phi, bad un buh ïa ki ha lade, ïa ki kali jong u, bad ban long ki nongshong kulai ha u; bad ban phet ha khmat ki kali jong u:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad un buh ïa ki ha lade ban long ki rangbah ïa ki hajar, bad ki rangbah ïa ki sanphew; bad ban lur ïa ka lyngkha jong u, bad ban ot ïa ka jingot jong u, bad ban thaw ïa ki atiar ïapom jong u, bad ki atiar ïa ki kali ïapom jong u.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad un shim ïa ki khun kynthei jong phi ban long ki apothekari, bad ki nongshet ja shet jyntah, bad ki nongshet kpu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad un shim ïa ki lyngkha jong phi, bad ïa ki brisoh Waiñ jong phi, bad ïa ki brisoh Olib jong phi, ki babha tam keiñ, bad un ai noh ha ki shakri jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad un shim ïa kaba shiphew na ki symbai jong phi, bad na ki brisoh Waiñ jong phi, bad un ai ha ki myntri jong u, bad ha ki shakri jong u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad un shim ïa ki shakri shynrang jong phi, bad ïa ki shakri kynthei jong phi, bad ïa ki babha tam na ki samla jong phi, bad ïa ki kadda jong phi, bad un buh ha ka kam jong u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad un shim ïa kaba shiphew na ki langbrot jong phi: bad ma phi hi ruh phin long ki shakri jong u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ha kata ka sngi phin lynñiar noh namar uta u syiem jong phi uba phi la jied; bad U Trai un ym shahshkor ïa phi ha kata ka sngi.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> La kumta ruh, kita ki briew kim treh ban sngap ïa ka ktien u Samuel; bad ki la ïa-ong, “Em; hynrei, ngin ïoh da u syiem halor jong ngi;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ba ngi ruh ngin ïoh long kum kita ki jaid bynriew baroh; u syiem jong ngi un bishar ïa ngi, bad un mih shabar ha shuwa jong ngi, bad un ïaleh ïa ki jingïaleh thma jong ngi.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Samuel u la ïohsngew ïa ki ktien baroh ki jong kita ki briew, bad u la ïathuh ïa ki ha ki shkor jong U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Samuel, “To shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong ki, bad to thung da u syiem halor jong ki.” Bad u Samuel u la ong ha kita ki rangbah Israel, “To khie leit uwei pa uwei baroh sha la ka shnong ka shnong.”"
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la don u briew uba na ki Benjamin, uba kyrteng “u Kish”, u khun u Abiel, uba u khun u Seror, u khun u Bekhoreth, u khun u Aphiah, u khun u kynja Benjamin, uba khraw bor eh.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la don u khun, uba kyrteng “u Saul”, u samla uba itynnad bad babhabriew: bad na ki khun Israel ym shym la don uwei uba kham bhabriew ban ïa u; u la long uba ka rynïeng ba uno uno na kita ki briew u kot tang ha tyrpeng.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki kadda u Kish, u kpa u Saul ki la jah noh. Bad u Kish u la ong ha u Saul u khun jong u, “To ïalam bad me uwei na kine ki shakri, to khie ruh, da leit wad ïa kita ki kadda.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki la ïaid ïa ka ri lum Ephraim, bad ki la ïaid ïa ka ri Shalisha, te kim shem ïa ki: ynda kumta, ki la ïaid ïa ka ri Shalim, hangta ruh kim don: te ki la ïaid ïa ka ri jong ki Benjamin, hynrei, kim shem ïa ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba ki la poi sha ka ri Suph, u Saul u la ong ïa la u shakri uba don lem bad u, “Ïa ngin ïaleit wan noh; ïoh u kpa jong nga un da wai noh shaphang ki kadda, u khuslai pynban ïa ngi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U te u la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, ha kane ka shnong don u briew u jong U Blei, bad u long u briew uba donburom; baroh kat kaba u ong ka jia long shisha: ïa ngin ïaleit shata; lehse un ïathuh ïa ngi ïa ka lynti kaba ngi dei ban leit.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Saul u la ong ïa la u shakri, “Ha khmih, lada ngi leit, ngin leit lam da ei ha uta u briew? naba u kpu u la lut noh na ki pliang jong ngi, bad ym don kawei pat ka jingai ban leit lam ha uta u briew jong U Blei: ngi don aïu?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te uta u shakri u la ïathuh pat ha u Saul, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga don ha la ka kti shi pawa shekel u sbai: da uta ngan ai ïa uta u briew jong U Blei, ba un ïathuh ha ngi ïa ka lynti jong ngi.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> (Mynnor ha Israel, u briew haba u leit ban ïakylli na U Blei, u la ju ong kumne, “Ale ngin ïaleit sha u nongïohi:” namar uta ïa uba khot mynta “u Nongïathuhlypa” la ju khot mynno mynno “u Nongïohi”).",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Kumta, u Saul u la ong ïa la u shakri, “Me la ïathuh bha; ïa, ngin ïaleit.” Kumta, ki la leit sha kata ka shnong ha kaba u la don uta u briew jong U Blei.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te katba ki dang ïakiew ïa ka thiep sha kata ka shnong, ki la ïashem ïa ki samla kynthei kiba dang ïamih ban leit tong um bad ki la kylli ïa ki, “Uta u nongïohi u don hangne?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki la ïathuh ïa ki, bad ki la ong, “U don; ha khmih, u ha pyrshah jong phi: to da pynkloi, namar ha kane ka sngi u la wan sha shnong; naba u paidbah u don ka jingkñia mynta ka sngi ha ka jaka jrong:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> haba phi dang shu poi shapoh ka shnong, phin shem ïa u kumne kumne, haba um pat leit kiew sha kata ka jaka jrong ban bam: naba ki briew kin ym bam tad ynda u la poi ma u, namar un kyrkhu ma u ïa ka jingkñia; hadien kata, kin bam kita ïa kiba la khot. Namar kata, to leit kiew; namar dei hamar kane ka por ba phin shem ïa u.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ki la leit kiew sha kata ka shnong; bad haba ki la poi hapdeng ka shnong, ha khmih, u Samuel u dang wan ïashem bad ki, ba un sa leit kiew sha kata ka jaka jrong.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te U Trai, shi sngi mynshuwa kaba poi u Saul, U la lah ïathuh ha ka shkor u Samuel, U da ong,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Lashai hamar kane ka por ngan phah sha me ïa u briew uba na ka ri Benjamin, te men pynsleh ïa u ban long u nongïalam halor ki briew jong nga ki Israel, bad un pyllait ïa ki briew jong nga na ka kti ki Philistia: namar nga la khmih ïa la ki briew, naba ka jinglynñiar jong ki ka la poi sha nga.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad haba u Samuel u la ïohi ïa u Saul, U Trai u la ong ha u, “Ha khmih uta u briew uba nga la ïathuh ha me shaphang jong u! une keiñ u ban synshar halor ki briew jong nga.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Saul u la leit hajan u Samuel ha ka khyrdop, bad u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to ïathuh ha nga hangno ka ïing u nongïohi.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ïathuh ha u Saul, bad u la ong, “Nga, nga long u nongïohi: to khie leit kiew ha shuwa jong nga sha kata ka jaka jrong, namar phin bam jingbam lem bad nga ha kane ka sngi: te lashai mynstep ngan pyllait noh ïa me, bad ngan ïathuh ha me ïa kaba ha ka dohnud jong me baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te shaphang kita ki kadda jong me kiba la jah noh la lai sngi mynta, wat khuslai shaphang jong ki; naba la shem ïa ki. Bad kita kiei kiei ki babha baroh ha Israel ki dei ïano? Ym dei ïa me, bad ïa baroh ka ïing u kpa jong me?”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Saul u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Nga ngam long u Benjamin, uba na ka barit tam na ki jaid Israel? bad ka kur jong nga ka barit tam na ki kur ka jaid Benjamin? balei te me kren kumta ïa nga?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad u Samuel u la shim ïa u Saul bad ïa uta u shakri jong u, bad u la wallam ïa ki sha kata ka kamra, bad u la pynshong ïa ki ha ka jaka kaba kham donnam hapdeng kita ïa kiba la khot, kiba la don kumba laiphew ngut ki briew.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong ha u nongshet, “Wallam ïa kata ka tukra kaba nga la ai ïa me, ïa kaba nga la ong ïa me, ‘To buh kyrpang.’ ”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad uta u nongshet u la shim ïa kata ka kti, bad kata kaba la don ha ka, bad u la buh ïa ka ha khmat u Saul. Bad u Samuel u la ong, “Ha khmih ïa kata kaba la buh tyngkai! to buh ha khmat jong me, bad to bam; naba hamar kane ka por la sumar ïa ka ha me, naduh kaba nga la ong, ‘Nga la khot ïa ki briew.’ ” Kumta, u Saul u la bam lem bad u Samuel ha kata ka sngi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba ki la ïawan hiar sha shnong na kata ka jaka jrong, u la ïakren bad u Saul halor ïing.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te ki la khie la dang step: bad hamar ba dang mih ka sngi, u Samuel u la khot ïa u Saul shalor ïing, u da ong, “Khie, ba ngan leit on lynti ïa me.” Bad u Saul u la khie, bad ki la leit mih noh baroh ar ngut, ma u bad u Samuel.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te katba ki dang ïahiar arsut ha ka bakut ka shnong, u Samuel u la ong ha u Saul, “Ong ïa une u shakri ba un nang leit sha shuwa jong ngi, (kumta u la nang leit,) hynrei, to ap ma me khyndiat mynta, te ngan pynsngew ha me ïa ka ktien U Blei.”"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Samuel u la shim shi tyndong ka umphniang, bad u la theh ïa ka halor ka khlieh jong u, bad u la doh ïa u, bad u la ong, “Hato U Trai um shym la pynsleh ïa me ban long u nongïalam halor ka bynta jong u?",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mynta ka sngi keiñ ynda me la leit noh na nga, men shem ïa ar ngut ki briew hajan ka jingtep ka Rakhel, ha ka pud Benjamin ha Selsah; bad kin ong ïa me, ‘La shem ïa kita ki kadda ïa kiba me la leit wad: te ha khmih, u kpa jong me u la wai noh shaphang ki kadda, bad u khuslai shaphang jong phi, u da ong, “Ngan leh kumno shaphang u khun jong nga?” ’",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Nangta te men nang leit, bad men poi sha u dieng Sning Tabor, bad hangta kin ïashem bad me lai ngut ki briew kiba leit kiew ha U Blei sha Bethel, uwei u da rah lai tylli ki khun blang, uwei pat u da rah lai tylli ki kpu, bad uwei pat u da rah shi lywa ka Waiñ:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> te kin khublei ïa me, bad kin ïa-ai ïa me ar tylli ki kpu; ma me ruh men shim ïa ki na ka kti jong ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hadien kata, men poi sha u lum U Blei, ha kaba don ka karod ki Philistia: te ynda me la poi shata sha ka shnong, men ïashem bad u paidbah ki nongïathuhlypa ki da hiar na kata ka jaka jrong, ki da don ruh ha shuwa jong ki ka bela, bad ka kanjari, bad ka sharati, bad ka duitara de; ba ki dang ïathuhlypa:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad U Mynsiem U Trai un wan jur ha me, bad ma me hi ruh men ïathuhlypa lem bad ki, bad yn pynkylla kum uwei pat u briew ïa me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ynda kin jia kine ki dak ïa me, to leh katba me shem lad; namar U Blei u don ryngkat bad me.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad men leit hiar ha shuwa jong nga sha Gilgal; bad ha khmih, nga ruh ngan sa wan hiar sha me, ïa ka ban ainguh da ki jingainguh thang, bad ban kñia ïa ki jingkñia pynïasuk: hynñiew sngi men ap, tad ynda ngan wan sha me, bad ngan sa ïathuh ïa me ïa kaba men leh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba u la phai dien ban leit noh na u Samuel, U Blei u la ai ha u da kawei pat ka dohnud: te kita ki dak baroh ki la jia long ha kata ka sngi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ki la poi shata sha uta u lum, ha khmih, u paidbah ki nongïathuhlypa ki la ïashem bad u; bad U Mynsiem U Blei u la wan jur ha u ruh, bad u la ïathuhlypa hapdeng jong ki.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te baroh kiba ju ithuh ïa u mynshuwa ki la ïohi, te ha khmih, u ïathuhlypa hapdeng kita ki nongïathuhlypa, te kita ki briew ki la ïakren paralok, “Kaei kane kaba la wan jia ïa u khun u Kish? Pleng u Saul ruh u don hapdeng ki nongïathuhlypa?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te uwei uba nangta u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Hynrei, u kpa jong ki u long uei?” Namar kata, ka la wan long ka pharshi, “Pleng u Saul ruh u don hapdeng ki nongïathuhlypa?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad haba u la wai noh kaba ïathuhlypa, u la wan poi sha kata ka jaka jrong.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u kñi u Saul u la ong ha u bad ha u shakri jong u, “Shano phi la leit?” U te u la ïathuh, “Ban wad ïa kita ki kadda: te haba ngi la ïohi ba ym shem ïa ki, ngi la leit poi sha u Samuel.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u kñi u Saul u la ïathuh, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to ïathuh ha nga, u Samuel u la ong aïu ïa phi.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Saul u la ïathuh ha la u kñi, “U la ïathuh skhem ha ngi ba la lah shem ïa kita ki kadda.” Hynrei, ïa kata ka ktien shaphang ka jinglong syiem, kaba u la kren u Samuel, um shym ïathuh ha u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Samuel u la khot lang ïa ki paidbah ha U Trai sha Mispah;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad u la ong ha ki khun Israel, “Kumne u ong U Trai, uba U Blei ki Israel, ‘Nga la wallam noh ïa ki Israel na ka ri Ijipt, bad nga la pyllait noh ïa phi na ka kti ki nong Ijipt, bad na ka kti ki hima baroh kiba la banbeiñ ïa phi:’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> phi te ha kane ka sngi phi la kyntait ïa U Blei jong phi, uba ma u hi u ju pynim ïa phi na ki jingjynjar jong phi baroh bad na ki jingkhuslai jong phi baroh; bad phi la ong ha u, ‘Em, hynrei, men thung syiem halor jong ngi.’ Mynta te namar kata, to ïeng ha khmat U Trai ha la ki jaid ki jaid, bad ha la ki hajar hajar.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te haba u Samuel u la pynwan hajan ïa ki jaid Israel baroh, la bat ïa ka jaid Benjamin.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Haba la pynwan hajan ïa ka jaid Benjamin ha la ki kur ki kur, la bat ïa ka kur u Matri: bad la bat ïa u Saul u khun u Kish; te haba ki la wad ïa u, kim shem ïa u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Namar kata, ki la kylli shuh ïa U Trai, “La uta u briew un wan pat shane ne em?” Bad U Trai u la ïathuh, “Ha khmih, u rieh ïa lade hapdeng kita ki jingbuh.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki la phet bad ki la wallam noh ïa u nangta; te haba u la ïeng hapdeng kita ki briew, u la long uba ka rynïeng ba ki briew baroh ki kot tang ha tyrpeng.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ong ha kita ki briew baroh, “Phi ïohi ïa uba u la jied U Trai, ba ym don uba kum ma u hapdeng ki briew baroh?” Te kita ki briew baroh ki la ïarisa, bad ki la ïa-ong, “To un im u syiem.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u Samuel u la ïathuh ïa ka rukom jong ka hima ha kita ki briew, bad u la thoh ïa ka ha ka kitab, bad u la buh ïa ka ha khmat U Trai. Bad u Samuel u la pyllait noh ïa ki briew baroh, uwei pa uwei sha la ïing la ïing.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad u Saul ruh u la leit noh sha la ïing sha Gibeah; bad u paidbah, kiba U Blei u la ktah ïa ki dohnud jong ki, ki la leit lem bad u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, don ki khun u Belial kiba la ïa-ong, “Kumno une un pynim ïa ngi?” Bad ki la beiñ ïa u, bad kim shym wallam ka jingai sngewbha ïa u. Hynrei, u, u la leh kum bym ïohsngew."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Nahash u nong Ammon u la leit kiew, bad u la sher dara ïaleh pyrshah ïa ki Jabesh-gilead: te ki nong Jabesh-gilead ki la ïa-ong ha u Nahash, “To pynlong ka jutang bad ngi, te ngin shakri ïa me.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Nahash u nong Ammon u la ong ha ki, “Ngan pynlong ïa ka bad phi da kumne, ba ngan ïoh khlaw noh ïa ka khmat kamon jong phi baroh; bad ngan buh ïa kane ba kan long kaba jahburom halor ki Israel baroh.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad ki tymmen basan jong ka Jabesh ki la ong ha u, “To shah ïa ngi hynñiew sngi, ba ngin ïoh phah ki nonglam-ktien sha ki phang ka Israel baroh: hadien kata te, lada ym don ban pynim ïa ngi, ngin mih shabar sha me.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kita ki nonglam-ktien ki la wan sha Gibeah u Saul, bad ki la kren ïa kine ki ktien ha kaba ïohsngew u paidbah: te u paidbah baroh u la pynjam ïa la ka ktien, bad u la ïam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ha khmih, u Saul u dang wan ñiah ïa ki masi na lyngkha; bad u Saul u la ong, “Na ka balei ba u ïam u paidbah?” Te ki la ïathuh ha u ïa ki ktien jong ki rangbah Jabesh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Mynsiem U Blei u la wan jur ha u Saul haba u la ïohsngew ïa kita ki ktien, bad ka jingbitar jong u ka la meh shikatdei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la shim shi jur ki masi dab, bad u la ot lyngkhot ïa ki, bad u la phah ïa ki ha ki phang ka Israel baroh da ka kti ki nonglam-ktien, u da ong, “Jar u ban ym wan mih hadien u Saul bad hadien u Samuel, kumta yn leh ha ki masi dab jong u.” Te ka jingsheptieng U Trai ka la hap ha u paidbah, bad ki la wan mih ryntih.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la kheiñ ïa ki ha Besek; te ki khun Israel ki la long laispah hajar bad ki rangbah Judah laiphew hajar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad ki la ong ha kita ki nonglam-ktien kiba la wan, “Kumne phin ong ha ki rangbah Jabesh-gilead, ‘Lashai, hamar ba la shit ka sngi, phin ïohlait im.’ ” Te kita ki nonglam-ktien ki la wan ïathuh ha ki Jabesh; ki te ki la sngewkmen.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar kata, ki Jabesh ki la ong, “Lashai ngin wan mih sha phi, bad phin leh ïa ngi ïa kiei kiei baroh katba phi ibit.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ha kaba lashai, u Saul u la pynlong lai kynhun ïa u paidbah; bad ki la wan hapdeng kata ka jaka shong dara ha ka jingap kaba mynstep, bad ki la pom ïa ki Ammon haduh kaba la shit ka sngi: te ïa kita kiba sah la pynsaphred, ba kumta ym don na ki kiba la sah ryngkat ar ngut.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U paidbah te u la ong ha u Samuel, “Uei uta uba la ong, ‘Une u Saul un synshar halor jong ngi?’ To wallam ïa kita ki briew, ba ngin pynïap ïa ki.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Saul u la ong, “Yn ym pynïap ïano ïano ha kane ka sngi: naba ha kane ka sngi, U Trai u la pynlong ka jingpynim ha Israel.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hangta u Samuel u la ong ha u paidbah, “Ïa ngin ïaleit sha Gilgal ban pynthymmai ïa ka jinglong syiem hangta.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u paidbah baroh u la leit sha Gilgal; bad hangta ki la pynlong syiem ïa u Saul ha khmat U Trai ha Gilgal; bad hangta ki la kñia ki jingkñia da ki jingainguh pynïasuk ha khmat U Trai; bad hangta u Saul bad ki rangbah Israel baroh ki la leh kmen shikatdei."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ong ha ki Israel baroh, “Ha khmih, nga la sngap ïa ka ktien jong phi ha kiei kiei baroh ba phi la ong ha nga, bad nga la thung syiem halor jong phi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te mynta, ha khmih, u syiem u ïaid ha khmat jong phi: nga te nga la tymmen bad nga la phuh 'ñiuhlieh; bad ha khmih, ki khun jong nga ki don bad phi: bad nga la ïaid ha khmat jong phi naduh ba nga dang samla haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ha khmih ïa nga: to sakhi pyrshah ïa nga ha khmat U Trai, bad ha khmat uba la sleh jong u: u masi dab jongno nga la shim? lane ka kadda jongno nga la shim? lane ïano nga la shukor? ïano nga la banbeiñ? lane na ka kti jongno nga la shim sap ban pynmatlah ïa la ki khmat da ka? te ngan buria ïa kata ha phi.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki te ki la ong, “Mem shym la shukor ïa ngi, lymne banbeiñ ïa ngi, lymne mem shym la shim ei ei na kti jongno jongno ruh.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “U Trai u long sakhi pyrshah ïa phi, bad uba la sleh jong U, u long sakhi ha kane ka sngi, ba phim shym la shem ei ei ha ka kti jong nga.” Ki ruh ki la ong, “U long sakhi keiñ.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ong ha u paidbah, “U long U Trai keiñ uba la thung ïa u Moses bad u Aaron, bad uba la wallam noh ïa ki kpa jong phi na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mynta te, to ïeng, ba ngan ïasaid bad phi ha khmat U Trai shaphang ki jinglehhok ki jong U Trai baroh, ïa kiba u la leh ha phi bad ha ki kpa jong phi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mynba u Jakob u la poi sha Ijipt, bad ki kpa jong phi ki la ïam ha U Trai, hangta U Trai u la phah ïa u Moses bad u Aaron, kiba la wallam noh ïa ki kpa jong phi na Ijipt, bad ki la pynshong ïa ki ha kane ka jaka.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki, hynrei, ki la klet noh ïa U Trai U Blei jong ki, U ruh U la die noh ïa ki ha ka kti u Sisera, u rangbah u paidïapom jong u Hasor, bad ha ka kti ki Philistia, bad ha ka kti u syiem ka Moab, bad ki la ïaleh thma ïa ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ki la ïam ha U Trai, bad ki la ong, ‘Ngi la leh pop, namar ba ngi la iehnoh noh ïa U Trai, bad ngi la shakri ïa ki Baal bad ki Ashtaroth: hynrei, mynta to pynim ïa ngi na ka kti ki nongshun jong ngi, te ngin shakri ïa me.’",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad U Trai u la phah ïa u Jerubbaal, bad u Bedan, bad u Jephthah, bad u Samuel, bad u la pyllait ïa phi na ka kti ki nongshun jong phi kylleng, bad phi la shong ha kaba suk.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad haba phi la ïohi ba u Nahash u syiem ki khun u Ammon u wan ïaleh ïa phi, phi la ong ha nga, ‘Em, hynrei, u syiem un synshar halor jong ngi:’ haba U Trai uba U Blei jong phi u la long u syiem jong phi ruh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Mynta te, khmih ïa u syiem ïa uba phi la jied, bad ïa uba phi la pan: bad ha khmih, U Trai u la buh syiem halor jong phi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Lada phin sheptieng ïa U Trai, bad shakri ïa u, bad sngap ïa ka ktien jong u, bad phin ym ïaleh pyrshah ïa ka hukum U Trai, kumta ma phi bad uta u syiem ruh uba synshar halor jong phi phin long ki nongbud ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong phi:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> hynrei, lada phin ym sngap ïa ka ktien U Trai, hynrei, phin ïaleh pyrshah ïa ka hukum U Trai, kumta ka kti U Trai kan long pyrshah ïa phi, kumba ka la long pyrshah ïa ki kpa jong phi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mynta, namar kata, to ïeng bad to khmih ïa kane kaba khraw, kaba U Trai un leh, ha kaba i ki khmat jong phi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Mynta kam long ka aïom ot Kew? Ngan khot kyrpad ha U Trai, te un phah ïa u pyrthat bad u slap: bad phin ïoh tip phin ïohi ruh ba kaba khraw ka jingbymman jong phi, kaba phi la leh ha khmat U Trai, ha kaba phi pan syiem.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kumta u Samuel u la khot kyrpad ha U Trai; te U Trai u la phah ïa u pyrthat bad u slap ha kata ka sngi: bad u paidbah baroh u la sheptieng shikatdei ïa U Trai bad ïa u Samuel.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u paidbah baroh u la ong ha u Samuel, “To duwai na ka bynta ki shakri jong me ha U Trai uba U Blei jong me, ba ngin ym ïap: namar ngi la pynlang ha ki pop jong ngi baroh sa kane ka jingbymman, ha kaba pan syiem.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> U Samuel te u la ong ha u paidbah, “Wat sheptieng: phi la leh shisha ïa kane ka jingbymman baroh: pynban, wat kiar noh na kaba bud ïa U Trai, hynrei, to shakri ïa U Trai da ka dohnud jong phi baroh;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad wat kiar noh: naba kumta phi la leit bud ïa kiei kiei kiba thala ki bym lah pynmyntoi lymne pyllait, naba ki long kiba thala keiñ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Naba U Trai un ym kyntait ïa la ki briew na ka bynta ka kyrteng kaba khraw jong u: namar U Trai u la ibit ban pynlong ïa phi u paidbah ha u hi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ma nga ruh, ngan nai ba ngan leh pop pyrshah ïa U Trai da kaba wai noh ban duwai na ka bynta jong phi: hynrei, ngan hikai ha phi ïa kata ka lynti ka babha bad kaba dei.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Tang ba phin sheptieng ïa U Trai, bad shakri ïa u ha kaba shisha da ka dohnud jong phi baroh: naba to pyrkhat ïa kaba katno kiba khraw u la leh na ka bynta jong phi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, lada phin ïai-leh bymman, yn pynjot noh ïa phi, ïa phi bad ïa u syiem jong phi.”"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Saul u la synshar shi snem: bad haba u la synshar ar snem halor ki Israel,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u Saul u la jied ha u, lai hajar ngut na ki Israel: ar hajar ki la don bad u Saul ha Mikhmash bad ha u lum Bethel, bad shi hajar bad u Jonathan ha Gibeah u Benjamin: te kita kiwei na u paidbah u la phah uwei uwei sha la ka jong ka jong ka ïingjaiñ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Jonathan u la pom ïa ka karod ki Philistia kaba ha Geba, te ki Philistia ki la ïohsngew ïa kata. Bad u Saul u la put da ka ronsing kylleng ka ri baroh, da kaba ong, “To kin ïohsngew ki Hebru.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad ki Israel baroh ki la ïohsngew ïa kaba ong ba u Saul u la pom ïa ka karod ki Philistia, bad ba ki Philistia ki la isih ïa ki Israel. Te ki paidbah ki la ïalum lang ban leit bud ïa u Saul sha Gilgal.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad ki Philistia ki la ïalum lang ban ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel, laiphew hajar ki kali ïapom, bad hynriew hajar ki shipai bashong kulai, bad u paidbah byllien kat u shyiap uba harud ha duriaw: bad ki la wan kiew bad ki la ïasher dara ha Mikhmash, shaphang mihngi na Beth-aben.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Haba ki rangbah Israel ki la ïohi ba ki la hap ha kaba khim, (naba u paidbah u la pisa eh,) hangta ki paidbah ki la buhrieh ïa lade ha ki krem, bad ha ki bniap, bad ha ki mawsiang, bad ha ki kut bajrong, bad ha ki thliew um.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad na ki Hebru don kiba la leit sha shiliang ka Jordan sha ka ri Gad bad Gilead; u Saul te u dang sah ha Gilgal, bad kita ki paidbah baroh ki la bud ïa u ki da kyiuh that that.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u la ap hynñiew sngi, haduh kata ka por ba la buh da u Samuel; hynrei, u Samuel um pat poi sha Gilgal, bad kita ki paidbah ki la ïasakma noh na u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Saul u la ong, “To wallam hangne ha nga ïa ka jingainguh thang bad ïa ki jingainguh pynïasuk.” Bad u la ainguh ïa kata ka jingainguh thang.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba u dang shu lah ainguh ïa kata ka jingainguh thang, ha khmih, u Samuel u la wan; bad u Saul u la mih ïa ka ban leit tan ïa u, ba un ïoh khublei ïa u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ong, “Me la leh aïu?” Bad u Saul u la ïathuh, “Namar ba nga la ïohi ba ki briew ki la sakma na nga, bad ba mem wan ha kita ki sngi ba la buh, bad ba ki Philistia ki la ïalum lang ha Mikhmash;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> namar kata, nga la ong, ‘Mynta kine ki Philistia kin wan hiar ha nga sha Gilgal, bad nga ruh ngam shym ïoh kyrpad ïa ka jingisynei U Trai:’ namar kata, nga la nud, bad nga la ainguh ïa ka jingainguh thang.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong ha u Saul, “Me la leh bieit: mem shym la sumar ïa ka hukum U Trai uba U Blei jong me, ïa kaba u la hukum ïa me: namar U Trai toi un da pynskhem mynta ïa ka jinglong syiem jong me halor ki Israel junom.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, mynta, ka jinglong syiem jong me kan ym neh: U Trai u la wad ha u ïa u briew uba katba kum ka dohnud jong U hi, bad U Trai u la thung ïa uta ban long u nongïalam halor ki briew jong U, namar ma me mem shym la sumar ïa kata kaba U Trai u la hukum ïa me.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ïeng, bad u la leit kiew na Gilgal sha Gibeah u Benjamin. Te u Saul u la ñiew ïa kita ki briew kiba sah ryngkat bad u, kumba hynriewspah ki rangbah.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u Saul, bad u Jonathan u khun jong u, bad kita ki briew kiba sah ryngkat bad ki, ki la shong ha Geba u Benjamin: hynrei, ki Philistia ki la shong dara ha Mikhmash.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad ki la mih noh na ka jaka shong dara ki Philistia ki nonglute lai kynhun: kawei ka kynhun ka la phai sha ka lynti kaba lam sha Ophrah, ha ka ri Shual:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad kawei pat ka kynhun ka la phai sha ka lynti Beth-horon: bad kata kawei ka kynhun ka la phai sha lynti jong kata ka pud kaba hiar arsut sha ka them Seboim shaphang ka ri khlaw keiñ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ha ka ri Israel baroh ym shym don kamar: namar ki Philistia ki la ong, “Ïoh ba kine ki Hebru kin thaw ha ki, ki waitlam lane ki sum”:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hynrei, ki Israel baroh ki la ju leit hiar sha ki Philistia, ïa ka ban pynnep uwei uwei ïa la u phar, bad ïa la u nar lyngkor, bad ïa la u sdie, bad ïa la u mohkhiew;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> hynrei, ki la don syrti ïa ki mohkhiew, bad ïa ki nar lyngkor, bad ïa ki proh, bad ïa ki sdie; bad ïa ka ban thung nar ha u dieng tyndung.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumta, ha kata ka sngi ba ïaleh thma, ym shym shem ïa ka waitlam lymne sum ha ka kti jongno jongno na kita ki briew kiba bad u Saul bad u Jonathan: sa tang kita hi kiba la shem ha u Saul bad u Jonathan u khun jong u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ïa ka karod ki Philistia la pynmih noh sha ki phud wah Mikhmash."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha kawei ka sngi ka la jia, ba u Jonathan u khun u Saul u la ong ha uta u samla uba rah ïa ki atiar jong u, “Ïa, ngin ïaleit sha shiliang sha kata ka karod ki Philistia sha lyndet.” Hynrei, um shym ïathuh ïa la u kpa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Saul u la sah ha ka bakut eh ka Gibeah, hapoh u dieng soh Pong uba ha Migron: bad kita ki briew kiba bad u, ki la don kumba hynriewspah ki rangbah;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad u Ahijah, u khun u Ahitub, uba u hynmen u Ikhabod, u khun u Phinehas, uba u khun u Eli, u lyngdoh U Trai ha Sheiloh, u phong ïa ka ephod. Te kita ki paidbah kim shym tip ba u Jonathan u la leit noh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te hapdeng kita ki phud wah, ha kiba u Jonathan u la pyrshang ban ryngkang sha kata ka karod ki Philistia, la don u mawsiang uba riat eh ha kawei ka liang, bad u mawsiang uba riat eh ha kawei pat ka liang: te ka kyrteng uwei ka la long “Boses”, bad ka kyrteng uta uwei “Seneh”.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ka ranab jong uwei ka la don shaphang shatei ha marpyrshah ka Mikhmash, bad ka jong uta uwei na shathie ha marpyrshah ka Geba.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Jonathan u la ong ha uta u samla uba rah ïa ki atiar jong u, “Ïa ngin ïaryngkang sha kata ka karod jong kine kiba khlem otsher: lehse U Trai un ïatrei lem bad ngi: namar ym don ka jingwit ïa U Trai ban pynim da ki babun lane da ki bakhyndiat.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te uta uba rah ïa ki atiar jong u, u la ong ha u, “To leh ïa kiei kiei baroh katba don ha ka dohnud jong me; to phai, ha khmih nga don ryngkat bad me katba mon ka dohnud jong me.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Jonathan te u la ong, “Ha khmih, ngin ïaryngkang sha kine ki briew, bad ngin pynpaw ïa lade ha ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Lada kin ong kumne ïa ngi, ‘To da ap tad ynda ngin wan sha phi;’ kumta ngin sah ha la ka jaka, bad ngin ym leit kiew sha ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, lada kin ong kumne, ‘To wan kiew sha ngi’; kumta ngin leit kiew: namar U Trai u la aiti noh ïa ki ha ka kti jong ngi: bad kane kan long ka dak ïa ngi.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad ki la pynpaw ïa lade baroh ar ngut ha kata ka karod ki Philistia: bad kita ki Philistia ki la ong, “Ha khmih, kita ki Hebru ki mih noh na kita ki thliew ha kiba ki la buhrieh ïa lade.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad kita ki briew kiba na kata ka karod ki la ïathuh ha u Jonathan bad ha uta uba rah ïa ki atiar jong u, bad ki la ong, “Wan kiew artet sha ngi, te ngin pyni ei ei ha phi.” Bad u Jonathan u la ong ha la u nongrah atiar, “Ale, bud ïa nga artet: namar U Trai u la aiti noh ïa ki ha ka kti ki Israel.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u Jonathan u la par artet da la ki kti bad da la ki kjat, bad uta uba rah ïa ki atiar jong u, u bud na shadien: bad ki la kyllon ïap ha khmat u Jonathan; bad uta uba rah ïa ki atiar u la pynïap na shadien jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te kata ka jingpynïap ka banyngkong, kaba u Jonathan bad u nongrah atiar jong u ki la pynlong, ka la long arphew ngut ki briew, ha kumba shiteng lynter ka nur lyngkor ha shi bigah ka khyndew.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad la don ka jingkyiuh ha ka jaka shong dara, ha lyngkha, bad hapdeng ki briew baroh; kata ka karod, bad kita ki nonglute, ki ruh ki la kyiuh: bad ka khyndew ruh ka la khynñiuh; kumta ka la long ka jingkyiuh ka bakhraw eh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad ki nongap phira jong u Saul ha Gibeah u Benjamin ki la khmih; te ha khmih, u paidbah u la ïasaphred noh, bad ki la phet shane bad shawei.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, u Saul u la ong ha kita ki briew kiba bad u, “To ñiew mynta, bad to khmih uei uba la leit noh na ngi.” Te haba ki la ñiew, ha khmih, u Jonathan bad uta u nongrah atiar jong u kim don hangta.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Saul u la ong ha u Ahijah, “To wallam shane ïa ka synduk U Blei,” namar ka synduk U Blei ka la don bad ki khun Israel ha kata ka por.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te katba u Saul u dang ïakren bad uta u lyngdoh, kata ka jingkhihwin kaba ha ka jaka shong dara ki Philistia ka dang don bad ka la nang khraw: bad u Saul u la ong ha uta u lyngdoh, “Kynran noh ïa la ka kti.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Saul bad kita ki briew baroh kiba bad u, ki la ïalum lang, bad ki la wan sha ka thma: te ha khmih, ka waitlam jong uwei pa uwei ka la ïaleh ïa la u lok, bad ka la don ka jingpynjot kaba khraw eh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kita ki Hebru ruh kiba la don bad ki Philistia mynshuwa, kiba la leit kiew lem bad ki sha kata ka jaka shong dara na ka ri kylleng, ki ruh ki la kylla ban long ryngkat bad kita ki Israel kiba bad u Saul bad u Jonathan.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Kumjuh ruh kita ki rangbah Israel baroh kiba la buhrieh ïa lade ha ri lum Ephraim, haba ki la ïohsngew ba ki la phet ïap ki Philistia, ki ruh ki la beh eh nadien jong ki ha kata ka thma.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta U Trai u la pynim ïa ki Israel ha kata ka sngi: bad kata ka jingïaleh thma ka la ïaid sha shiliang haduh Beth-aben.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki rangbah Israel ki la pisa ha kata ka sngi: naba u Saul u la pynsmai ïa ki briew, u da ong, “Long ba la tim ïa uta u briew uba bam jingbam haduh ba la janmiet, ba ngan ïoh pynhiar kput halor ki nongshun jong nga.” Kumta ym shym don uwei na kita ki briew uba la mad jingbam ei ei.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad kita ki briew baroh ki la poi sha kawei ka khlaw; bad ka la don ka ngap halor ka khyndew.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te haba kita ki briew ki la poi sha kata ka khlaw, ha khmih, ka ngap ka la jaw noh: hynrei, ym shym don uwei u briew uba la rah ïa la ka kti ha la ka shyntur; naba ki briew ki la sheptieng ïa kata ka jingsmai.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, u Jonathan um shym ïohsngew haba u kpa jong u, u la pynsmai ïa ki briew: namar kata, u la pynmih ïa ka tduh uta u dieng uba ha ka kti jong u, bad u la wieh ïa u ha ka rewngap, bad u la rah ïa la ka kti ha la ka shyntur; te ki khmat jong u ki la shai.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te uwei na kita ki briew u la ïathuh, bad u la ong, “U kpa jong me u la hukum skhem ïa ki briew da ka jingsmai, u da ong, ‘Long ba la tim ïa uta u briew u ban bam jingbam ha kane ka sngi.’ Te ki briew ki la sngewlwait.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Jonathan u la ong, “U kpa jong nga u la pynshitom ïa ka ri: khmih mynta, nga kyrpad ïa phi, kumno ba la pynshai ïa ki khmat jong nga, namar ba nga la mad khyndiat na kane ka ngap.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Katno tam te, lada ha kane ka sngi ki briew ki la ïoh ban bam katba mon na kata ka jinglute na ki nongshun jong ki, ïa kaba ki la ïoh? kam la long ka jingpynïap kaba kham khraw shikatdei hapdeng kine ki Philistia?”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te ki la pynïap ïa ki Philistia ha kata ka sngi naduh Mikhmash haduh Aijalon: bad ki briew ki la sngewlwait eh.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad kita ki briew ki la kynrup ïa ka jinglute, bad ki la shim ïa ki langbrot, bad ïa ki masi, bad ïa ki khun masi, bad ki la shohdoh ïa ki halor ka khyndew: bad kita ki briew ki la bam ïa ki lem bad ka snam.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïathuh ha u Saul, ki ïa-ong, “Ha khmih, kine ki briew ki leh pop ïa U Trai, ha kaba ki bam lem bad ka snam.” Te u la ong, “Phi la leh bymman: pyntyllun sha nga ïa u maw baheh ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u Saul u la ong, “To ïaphriang ïa lade hapdeng kine ki briew, bad ong ha ki, ‘To wallam shane sha nga uwei uwei ïa la u masi, bad uwei uwei ïa la ka langbrot, bad pynïap ïa ki hangne, bad bam: bad to wat leh pop ïa U Trai da kaba phi bam lem bad ka snam.’ ” Bad ha kata hi ka miet kita ki briew baroh ki la wallam lem bad ki uwei uwei ïa la u masi, bad ki la shohdoh ïa ki hangta.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u Saul u la tei ïa ka duwan ha U Trai: kata ka la long ka duwan ka banyngkong ba u la tei ha U Trai.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te u Saul u la ong, “To ngin ïahiar nadien kine ki Philistia mynmiet, bad ngin lute ïa ki haduh ba kan da shai mynstep, bad ngin ym pynsah uwei ruh na ki.” Ki te ki la ong, “To leh ïa kaba me ibit.” Te uta u lyngdoh u la ong, “To ngin ïaleit hajan shane sha U Blei.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Bad u Saul u la kylli na U Blei, “Ngan leit hiar ne em hadien kine ki Philistia? ma me ruh men aiti noh ne em ïa ki ha ka kti ki Israel?” Hynrei, um shym phai ktien ha u ha kata ka sngi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u Saul u la ong, “To ïawan hajan shane, phi ki nongïalam baroh jong kine ki briew: bad to wad to khmih ruh ha-ei ka la don kane ka pop ha kane ka sngi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Naba, katba im U Trai, uba pynim ïa ki Israel, la kane ka don wat ha u Jonathan u khun jong nga, da kaba ïap un ïap shisha.” Hynrei, na kita ki briew baroh ym shym don uwei uba la phai ktien ïa u.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> U te u la ong ha ki Israel baroh, “To long ma phi ha kawei ka liang, te ma nga bad u Jonathan u khun jong nga ngin ïalong ha kawei pat ka liang.” Bad kita ki briew ki la ong ha u Saul, “To leh katba me ibit.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Namar kata, u Saul u la ong ha U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, “To pyni ïa ka hok.” Te la bat ïa u Saul bad u Jonathan: hynrei, kita ki briew ki la lait.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad u Saul u la ong, “To pynnoh ïa ka jingkhalai hapdeng jong nga bad u Jonathan u khun jong nga.” Bad la bat ïa u Jonathan.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ynda kumta, u Saul u la ong ha u Jonathan, “To ïathuh ha nga me la leh aïu.” Bad u Jonathan u la ïathuh ha u, bad u la ong, “Tang kaba shu mad khyndiat ka ngap da ka tduh uta u dieng uba la don ha ka kti jong nga; te ha khmih, ka la dei ïa nga ban ïap pleng.”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> U Saul te u la ong, “U Blei un leh kumta bad tam ruh: naba men ïap shisha, ko Jonathan.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te kita ki briew ki la ong ha u Saul, “Hato un ïap u Jonathan, uba la pynlong ka jingpynim kaba khraw kat kane ha Israel? Kan ym long kumta, em: katba im U Trai, in ym hap iwei na ki 'ñiuh khlieh jong u ha ka khyndew; namar u la trei ryngkat bad U Blei ha kane ka sngi.” Kumta, kita ki briew ki la pynim ïa u Jonathan, ba um shym ïap.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Kumta, u Saul u la leit kiew noh na kaba beh ïa ki Philistia: bad ki Philistia ki la leit noh sha la ka jong ka jaka.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Te haba u Saul u la shimti ïa ka jinglong syiem halor ki Israel, u la ïaleh thma ïa la ki nongshun baroh kylleng, ïa ki Moab, bad ïa ki khun u Ammon, bad ïa ka Edom, bad ïa ki syiem Sobah, bad ïa ki Philistia de: bad shano shano ba u la phai la ka khmat, u la jop.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Bad u leh shlur, bad u la pom ïa ki Amalek, bad u la pyllait ïa ki Israel na ki kti jong kita kiba lute ïa ki.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Te ki khun shynrang u Saul ki la long u Jonathan, bad u Ishbi, bad u Melkhi-shua de: bad ki kyrteng ki ar ngut ki khun kynthei jong u kine; ka kyrteng ka banyngkong “ka Merab”, bad ka kyrteng ka bakhatduh “ka Mikhal”:",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> bad ka kyrteng ka tnga u Saul, “ka Ahinoam” ka khun u Ahimaas: bad ka kyrteng u nongïalam u paidïapom jong u, “u Abner” u khun u Ner, u kñi u Saul.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Te u Kish u la long u kpa jong u Saul; bad u Ner u kpa u Abner u la long u khun u Abiel.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Bad la don ka jingïaleh thma kaba jur bad ki Philistia baroh ki sngi jong u Saul; bad haba u Saul u ïohi ïa uno uno u rangbah uba khlaiñ bad uba shlur u la ju shim ïa u ha lade."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong ha u Saul, “U Trai u la phah ïa nga ban pynsleh ïa me ban long syiem halor u paidbah jong u, halor ki Israel keiñ: mynta te, to men sngap ïa ka jingsawa ki ktien U Trai.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Kumne u ong U Trai ki paid, ‘Nga la kynmaw ïa kaba u la leh u Amalek ha ki Israel, kumno ba u la ïeng ïaleh ïa u ha ka lynti, mynba u la wan mih noh na ka ri Ijipt.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> To khie mynta, bad to pom ïa ki Amalek, bad to pynjot noh khoit ïa kiei kiei baroh katba ki don, bad wat pynim ïa ki; hynrei, to men pynïap ïa ki bad shynrang bad kynthei, bad khynnah bad khunlung ba dang buiñ, bad masi bad langbrot, ki ut bad ki kadda.’ ”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Saul u la lum khar paid, bad u la ñiew ïa ki ha Telaim, arspah hajar ki briew ba-ïaleh na tbian, bad shiphew hajar ki Judah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Saul u la wan sha ka nongbah ki Amalek, bad u la ap thap ha ka them.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Saul u la ong ha ki Ken, “Khie noh, kynriah noh, leit hiar noh napdeng kine ki Amalek, ba ïoh ngan pynjot noh ïa phi lem bad ki: namar phi la leh isynei ïa ki khun Israel baroh, mynba ki la wan mih noh na ka ri Ijipt.” Kumta ki Ken ki la kynriah noh napdeng kita ki Amalek.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Saul u la pom ïa ki Amalek naduh Habilah haduh ban da poi sha Shur, kaba marpyrshah ka ri Ijipt.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u la kem im ïa u Agag u syiem ki Amalek, bad u la pynïap noh khoit ïa kita ki briew baroh da ka syrti waitlam.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, u Saul bad kita ki briew ki la ri im ïa u Agag, bad ïa ki babha tam na ki langbrot, bad na ki masi ïa kiba kham sngaid, bad ïa ki khun langbrot, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh ki babha, bad kim pynjot noh khoit ïa ki: hynrei, ïa kaei kaei baroh ka basniew bad ka bymdonkam, ïa kata ki la pynjot noh khoit.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ka ktien U Trai ka la wan ha u Samuel, ka da ong,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> “Nga la kylla-ka-bamut ïa kaba nga la thung syiem ïa u Saul: namar u phai dien noh na kaba bud ïa nga, bad um shym pyndep ïa ki hukum jong nga.” Te u Samuel u la sngewsih eh; bad u la lynñiar ha U Trai baroh shi miet.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te haba u Samuel u la khie dang step ïa ka ban ïashem bad u Saul kum lashai, te la ïathuh ha u Samuel da kaba ong, “U Saul u la leit sha Karmel, bad ha khmih, u la thung mawbynna ïa lade, bad u la ïaid kylleng, bad u la nang leit, bad u la leit hiar sha Gilgal.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Samuel u la poi sha u Saul: bad u Saul u la ong ha u, “To U Trai un kyrkhu ïa me: nga la pyndep ïa kata ka hukum U Trai.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ong, “Haba kumta, kaei kane ka jingpah ki langbrot kaba ha ki shkor jong nga, bad kane ka jingpah ki masi kaba nga ïohsngew?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad u Saul u la ïathuh, “Ki la wallam ïa ki na ki Amalek: namar u paidbah u la pynim ïa ki babha tam na ki langbrot bad na ki masi, ïa ka ban kñia ha U Trai uba U Blei jong me.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong ha u Saul, “Ha sngap, ngan ïathuh te ha me ïa kaba U Trai u la kren ha nga mynhynne mynmiet.” U te u la ong, “To kren.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ong, “La me la long uba ñiew rit ïa lade, la pynlong ne em ïa me u nongïalam ïa ki jaid Israel? Bad U Trai u la pynsleh ïa me ban long syiem halor ki Israel.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U Trai te u la phah leit jingleit ïa me, bad u la ong, ‘To leit bad pynjot noh khoit ïa kita ki bapop, kita ki Amalek keiñ, bad to ïaleh pyrshah ïa ki ha ban da la pynduh noh ïa ki.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata te, balei ba mem shym la kohnguh ïa ka ktien U Trai, hynrei, me la kynrup sha kata ka jinglute, bad me la leh ïa ka basniew ha khmat U Trai?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Saul u la ong ha u Samuel, “Da shisha nga la kohnguh ïa ka ktien U Trai, bad nga la leit ha kata ka lynti kaba U Trai u la phah ïa nga, bad nga la wallam ïa u Agag u syiem ki Amalek, bad nga la pynjot noh khoit ïa kita ki Amalek.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, shisha u paidbah u la shim na kata ka jinglute, ïa ki langbrot bad ïa ki masi, ïa ki babha tam keiñ na kita kiba la dei ban pynjot, ïa ka ban kñia ha U Trai uba U Blei jong me ha Gilgal.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong, “U Trai u sngewbha ma ha ki jingainguh thang bad ha ki jingkñia kumba ha kaba kohnguh ïa ka ktien U Trai? Ha khmih, kaba kohnguh ka kham bha ban ïa ka jingkñia, bad kaba shahshkor ban ïa ka khleiñ ki 'lang sohmoh.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar ka jingleh kiat ka long kat ka pop ka jingleh byrtong hi, bad ka jingmutlop ka long kum kaba mane bleithaw bad ki teraph. Namar ba me la kyntait ïa ka ktien U Trai, ma u ruh u la kyntait ïa me na kaba long syiem.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Saul u la ong ha u Samuel, “Nga la leh pop: namar ba nga la palat ïa ka hukum U Trai, bad ïa ki ktien jong me: naba nga la sheptieng ïa ki paidbah, bad ba nga la kohnguh ïa ki ktien jong ki.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei mynta, nga kyrpad ïa me, to map ïa kane ka pop jong nga, bad to wan phai ryngkat bad nga, ba ngan ïoh mane ïa U Trai.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong ha u Saul, “Ngan ym leit phai bad me: naba me, me la kyntait ïa ka ktien U Trai, bad U Trai ruh u la kyntait ïa me na kaba long syiem halor ki Israel.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Bad haba u Samuel u la phai ïa ka ban leit noh, u ruh u la bat na ka rmiang ka jaiñkup jong u, bad ka la kad.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong ha u, “U Trai u la kad noh ïa ka hima Israel na me ha kane ka sngi, bad u la aiti noh ïa ka ha uwei u paramarjan jong me, uba kham bha ïa me.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ruh putet, uba Ka Bor ki Israel un ym lamler lymne kylla-ka-bamut; namar ma u um long u briew, ba un kylla-ka-bamut.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ynda kumta, u la ong, “Nga la leh pop: pynban, nga kyrpad ïa me, to burom ïa nga mynta, ha khmat ki tymmen basan ki paidbah jong nga, bad ha khmat ki Israel, bad to wan phai bad nga ba ngan ïoh mane ïa U Trai uba U Blei jong me.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumta, u Samuel u la phai pat hadien u Saul; bad u Saul u la mane ïa U Trai.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong, “To wallam noh shane sha nga ïa u Agag u syiem ki Amalek.” Bad u Agag u la wan sha u da kaba phuhmat. Bad u Agag u la ong, “Shisha ka jingkthang ka jingïap ka la leit noh.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong, “Kat kumba ka waitlam jong me ka la pynduh khun ïa ki kynthei, kumta ïa ka kmie jong me yn pynduh khun hapdeng ki kynthei.” Bad u Samuel u la shaiñ lyngkhot lyngkhai ïa u Agag ha khmat U Trai ha Gilgal.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ynda kumta, u Samuel u la leit noh sha Ramah; bad u Saul u la leit kiew sha la ïing sha Gibeah u Saul.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te u Samuel um shym wan shuh ban khmih ïa u Saul haduh ka sngi ka jingïap jong u; pynban, u Samuel u la ïambriew namar u Saul: bad U Trai u la kylla-ka-bamut ïa kaba u la thung syiem ïa u Saul halor ki Israel."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad U Trai u la ong ha u Samuel, “Men ïambriew ïa u Saul sa katno, haba nga, nga la kyntait ïa u na kaba long syiem halor ki Israel? To pyndap ïa kata ka reng jong me da ka umphniang, bad khie leit, ngan phah ïa me sha u Jesse u nong Bethlehem, naba nga la khreh ïa nga ïa u syiem napdeng ki khun shynrang jong u.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong, “Kumno ngan leit? Lada u Saul un ïohsngew, un pynïap ïa nga.” Bad U Trai u la ong, “To shim bad me da ka masi lud, bad ong, ‘Nga la wan ïa ka ban kñia ha U Trai.’",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad to khot ïa u Jesse sha kata ka jingkñia, te ngan sa pyntip ha me ïa kaba me dei ban leh: me ruh men pynsleh ïa nga ïa uta uba ngan sa ïathuh ha me.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Samuel u la leh ïa kata kaba la kren U Trai bad u la wan sha Bethlehem. Te kita ki tymmen basan kata ka shnong ki la sheptieng shikatdei haba ki la ïashem bad u, bad ki la ong, “Me wan ïa kaba suk?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U te u la ïathuh, “Ïa kaba suk keiñ: nga la wan ïa ka ban kñia ha U Trai: to pynkyntang ïa lade, bad wan bad nga sha kata ka jingkñia.” Bad u la pynkyntang ïa u Jesse bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong u, bad u la khot ïa ki sha kata ka jingkñia.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba ki la wan, u la khmih keiñ ïa u Eliab, bad u la ong, “Shisha uta uba la sleh jong U Trai u don ha khmat jong u.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la ong ha u Samuel, “Wat khmih ïa ka khmat jong u, lymne ïa ka jingjrong ka rynïeng jong u, namar nga la kyntait ïa u: naba U Blei um ju khmih kumba khmih u briew; naba u briew u ïohi tang ïa ka dur kaba shabar, hynrei, U Trai u ïohi ïa ka dohnud.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumta, u Jesse u la khot ïa u Abinadab, bad u la phah ïa u ban leit ha khmat u Samuel. U te u la ong, “U Trai um shym la jied ïa une ruh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta, u Jesse u la phah ïa u Shammah ban leit. U te u la ong, “Ïa une ruh U Trai um shym la jied.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jesse u la phah hynñiew ngut na ki khun shynrang jong u ban leit ha khmat u Samuel. U Samuel te u la ong ha u Jesse, “U Trai um shym la jied ïa kine.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Samuel u la ong ïa u Jesse, “Ki khun jong me baroh tang kine?” U te u la ong, “U dang sah sa u bakhatduh, te ha khmih, u sharai ïa ki langbrot.” Bad u Samuel u la ong ha u Jesse, “To phah bad wallam ïa u: namar ngin ym ïashong tad ynda u la wan ma u shane.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U te u la phah, bad u la wallam ïa u. Te u la long uba saw syntiew, bad uba bhabriew ka khmat bad uba ibha ban khmih ïa u. U Trai te u la ong, “To khie, to pynsleh ïa u: namar u long une keiñ.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Samuel u la shim ïa kata ka reng umphniang, bad u la pynsleh ïa u hapdeng kita ki hynmen jong u: bad U Mynsiem U Trai u la wan jur ha u Dabid naduh kata ka sngi. Ynda kumta, u Samuel u la khie, bad u la leit sha Ramah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, U Mynsiem U Trai u la kynriah noh na u Saul, bad u mynsiem bymman na U Trai u la pynsheptieng ïa u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad ki shakri u Saul ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Ha khmih, pleng u mynsiem bymman na U Blei u pynsheptieng ïa me.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> To ai te ba u kynrad jong ngi un hukum ïa la ki shakri, kiba ha khmat jong me, ba kin wad da u briew uba nang tem duitara: te kan jia, haba uta u mynsiem bymman uba na U Blei u wan ha me, ba u ruh un tem da la ka kti, bad me ruh men bha.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Saul u la ong ïa la ki shakri, “To pynwad ïa nga da u briew uba nang bha ban tem, bad to wallam ïa u ha nga.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te uwei na kita ki shakri u la ïathuh, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga la ïohi ïa uwei u khun u Jesse u nong Bethlehem, uba nang ha kaba tem bad uba khlaiñ bor, bad u long u nongïaleh thma, bad uba stad ktien, bad uba bhabriew lymphuin, bad U Trai ruh u don ryngkat bad u.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata, u Saul u la phah ïa ki nonglam-ktien sha u Jesse, bad u la ong, “To phah sha nga ïa u Dabid u khun jong me, uba bad ki langbrot.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Jesse u la shim shi khung u kpu, bad shi lywa ka Waiñ bad u khun blang, bad u la phah ïa ki ha u Dabid u khun jong u, sha u Saul.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Dabid u la wan ha u Saul, bad u la ïeng ha khmat jong u: u ruh u la ieit ïa u shikatdei: te u de u la long u nongrah atiar jong u.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Saul u la phah sha u Jesse, u da ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa u Dabid ban sah ha khmat jong nga; namar u la shem ïa ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong nga.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba uta u mynsiem bymman uba na U Blei u la wan ha u Saul, kumta u Dabid u la shim ïa ka duitara, bad u la tem da la ka kti: te kumta, la pynshait ïa u Saul, bad la pynbha ïa u, bad uta u mynsiem bymman u la kynriah noh na u."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la lum lang ïa la ki paidïapom ïa ka ban ïaleh thma, bad ki la ïalum lang ha Shokhoh, kaba ha Judah, bad ki la ïasher dara hapdeng Shokhoh bad Asekah, ha Ephes-dammim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Saul bad ki paidbah Israel ki la ïalum lang, bad ki la ïasher dara ha ka them Elah, bad ki la khreh riang ïa u paidïapom ban ïaleh ïa ki Philistia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la ïeng halor u lum ha kawei ka liang, bad ki Israel ki la ïeng halor u lum ha kawei pat ka liang: te la don ka them hapdeng jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te la wan mih u briew hapdeng jong ki na ka jaka shong dara ki Philistia, uba kyrteng “u Goliath”, na Gath, uba ka rynïeng jong u, hynriew pruh shi tda.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ka jingïada khlieh rnong ka la don ha ka khlieh jong u, bad u la phong da ka jingphong nar; te ka jingkhia kata ka jingphong ka la don san hajar shekel ka rnong.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad ki sop'jat rnong ki la don ha ki kjat jong u, bad ka stieh rnong hapdeng ki siang tyrpeng jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u dieng-thung-sum jong u la kat u khung u nongthain jaiñ: te u nar sum jong u, u la hynriewspah shekel ka jingkhia jong u: bad u nongrah stieh u la ïaid ha shuwa jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u la ïeng bad u la pyrta ïa ki paidïapom ki Israel, bad u la ong ha ki, “Balei phi ïamih ban khreh riang ïa la ki paidïapom? Nga ngam long u Philistia, phi ruh ki shakri u Saul? to jied ïa phi da u briew ban wan hiar sha nga.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Lada un lah ïaleh bad nga, bad pynïap ïa nga, kumta ngin long shakri ïa phi: hynrei, lada ngan lah ma nga ïa u, bad pynïap ïa u, te kumta ma phi phin long ki shakri jong ngi, bad phin shakri ïa ngi.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad uta u Philistia u la ong, “Nga la beiñ ïa ki paidïapom ki Israel ha kane ka sngi; to ai ïa u briew ha nga, ba ngin ïaleh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Haba u Saul bad ki Israel baroh ki la ïohsngew ïa kita ki ktien jong uta u Philistia, ki la khaw-eit, bad ki la sheptieng shikatdei.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Dabid u la long u khun jong u nong Ephrath na Bethlehem Judah, uba kyrteng u Jesse; bad u la don phra ngut ki khun shynrang: te ha ki sngi u Saul, ïa une u briew la ñiew riewtymmen hapdeng ki briew.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ki lai ngut ki khun ki banyngkong u Jesse ki la leit bad ki la bud ïa u Saul sha kata ka thma: te ki kyrteng kine ki lai ngut ki khun jong u kiba la leit sha kata ka thma, ki la long “u Eliab” u banyngkong, bad “u Abinadab” uba bud; bad “u Shammah” u balai.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Dabid u la long u bakhatduh; bad kita ki lai ngut ki hynmen ki la bud ïa u Saul.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Dabid u la ju ïaleit ïawan na u Saul ïa ka ban sharai ïa ki langbrot u kpa jong u ha Bethlehem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te uta u Philistia u la wan mih mynstep bad janmiet, bad u la pyni ïa lade sawphew sngi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Jesse u la ong ha u Dabid u khun jong u, “To shim mynta ha la ki hynmen shi ephah na une u Kew sdieh, bad kine ki shiphew tylli ki kpu, bad to leit lam kloi sha ka jaka shong dara ha la ki hynmen;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad to rah ïa kine ki shiphew tylli ki ktung dud ha uta u rangbah shihajar jong ki, bad to leit jngoh ïa la ki hynmen, la ki koit ki khiah ne em, bad to pyllait ïa ka bynda jong ki.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te u Saul, bad ki, bad kita ki paidbah Israel baroh, ki la don ha ka them Elah, ki da ïaleh thma bad kita ki Philistia.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Dabid u la khie dang step, bad u la iehnoh ïa kita ki langbrot bad u nongsumar, bad u la shim, bad u la leit, kumba la hukum u Jesse ïa u; te u la poi sha kata ka jaka shong dara, katba ki paidïapom ki dang ïaleit mih sha kata ka jaka ïaleh, bad ki da ïarisa ban sa ïaleh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Namar ki Israel bad ki Philistia ki la ïakhreh riang ïa la ki paidïapom, ki da ïaïeng marpyrshah.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Dabid u la iehnoh ïa kata ka jingkit jong u ha ka kti uta uba sumar ïa ki jingbuh, bad u la phet sha uta u paidïapom, bad u la poi bad u la khublei ïa la ki hynmen.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te katba u dang ïakren bad ki, ha khmih, uta u rangbah, uta u Philistia na Gath, uba kyrteng “u Goliath”, u la wan mih noh na ki paidïapom ki Philistia, bad u la kren ïa kita kijuh ki ktien: bad u Dabid u la ïohsngew ïa ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki paidbah Israel baroh, haba ki la ïohi ïa uta u briew ki la phet ïap noh na u, bad ki la sheptieng shikatdei.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad kita ki paidbah Israel ki la ïa-ong, “Phi la ïohi ne em ïa uta u briew uba la wan mih noh? shisha u la wan mih khnang ïa ka ban beiñ ïa ki Israel: te uta u briew u ban pynïap ïa u, u syiem un pynriewspah ïa u da ka spah kaba khraw, un ai kurim ruh ïa la ka khun ha u, bad un pynlong laitluid ïa ka ïing u kpa jong u ha Israel.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Dabid u la kren ha kita ki briew kiba ïeng hajan jong u, u da ong, “Yn leh aïu ïa uta u briew u ban pynïap ïa une u Philistia, bad u ban pynduh noh ïa kane kaba jahburom na Israel? naba uei une u Philistia uba khlem otsher, ba u beiñ ïa ki paidïapom jong U Blei u ba-im?”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te kita ki briew ki la ïathuh ha u da kata ka rukom, ki da ong, “Kumta keiñ yn leh ïa uta u briew u ban pynïap ïa u.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u Eliab u hynmen nyngkong jong u, u la ïohsngew haba u la kren ha kita ki briew; bad ka jingbitar u Eliab ka la meh lep ïa u Dabid, bad u la ong, “Me la wan hiar shane balei? bad me la iehnoh badno ïa kita ki khyndiat ki langbrot ha ka ri khlaw? Nga ithuh ïa ka jingsarong jong me, bad ïa ka jingrunar ka dohnud jong me; namar me la wan hiar khnang tang ba men ïohi ïa ka thma.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong, “Nga la leh aïu te? Balei ym don daw?”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u la phai noh na u sha uwei pat, bad u la ong ïa kajuh ka ktien: bad uta u paidbah u la ïathuh pat ha u da kijuh ki ktien kumba mynshuwa.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te haba la ïohsngew ïa kita ki ktien kiba u la kren u Dabid, ki la ïathuh pateng ïa ki ha khmat u Saul: u te u la phah khot ïa u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Saul, “Wat ai ba kan khaw-eit ka dohnud jongno jongno ruh namar uta: u shakri jong me un leit bad un ïaleh bad une u Philistia.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u Saul u la ong ha u Dabid, “Me mem lah ban mih pyrshah ïa une u Philistia ban ïaleh bad u: namar me, me dang samla, u te u long u riewïapom la myndang khynnah.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Saul, “U shakri jong me u la sumar ïa ki langbrot u kpa jong u: te ki la mih u sing bad ka dngiem, bad ki la kynrup ïa u khun langbrot na ka kynhun,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> te nga la bud nadien jong u, bad nga la shoh ïa u, bad nga la pyllait ïa u na ka shyntur jong u: te haba u la ïeng ïaleh pyrshah ïa nga, nga la kem ïa u na u 'ñiuh tmoh, bad nga la shoh ïa u, bad nga la pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kumta u shakri jong me u la pynïap ïa uta u sing bad ïa kata ka dngiem: te une u Philistia uba khlem otsher un long kum uwei na kita, namar ba u la beiñ ïa ki paidïapom jong U Blei u ba-im.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ruh, “U Trai uba la pynim ïa nga na ka kti u sing, bad na ka kti ka dngiem, uta keiñ, un pynim ïa nga na ka kti une u Philistia.” Te u Saul u la ong ha u Dabid, “Khie leit, bad U Trai un long ryngkat bad me.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u Saul u la pynphong ha u Dabid ïa ki jingkieng atiar jong u, bad u la buh ïa ka jingïada khlieh rnong ha ka khlieh jong u, bad u la pynphong ha u da ka jingphong nar.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te u Dabid u la woh ïa ka waitlam ha kata ka jingkieng atiar jong u, bad u la pyrshang ban ïaid: namar ba um shym mlien. Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Saul, “Ngam lah ïaid ha kine; namar ngam ju mlien.” Bad u Dabid u la loit noh ïa ki.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad u la shim ïa la u diengduh ha la ka kti, bad u la jied ha u na kata ka wah, san tylli ki maw kiba lyngkniap, bad u la thep ïa ki ha kata ka pla snieh u nongaplangbrot kaba u don, kata, ha ka ïarong keiñ; bad ka jingshat maw jong u ka ha ka kti jong u: te u la leit hajan uta u Philistia.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Bad uta u Philistia u la nang wan bad u la wan hajan u Dabid; bad uta u briew uba rah ïa ka stieh u la ïaid ha shuwa jong u.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te haba uta u Philistia u la khmih, bad ba u la ïohi ïa u Dabid, u la ibeiñ ïa u: naba u dang samla, bad uba saw syntiew, bad uba bhabriew.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad uta u Philistia u la ong ha u Dabid, “Nga, nga long u ksew, ba me wan ha nga da u diengduh?” Bad uta u Philistia u la tim ïa u Dabid da ki blei jong u.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Uta u Philistia u la ong ruh ha u Dabid, “Ale me sha nga, te ngan ai ïa ka doh jong me ha ki sim ka suiñ, bad ha ki mrad ka khyndew.”",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> U Dabid te u la ong ha uta u Philistia, “Me, me wan ha nga da ka waitlam, bad da u sum, bad da ka stieh: nga te nga wan sha me ha ka kyrteng U Trai ki paid, U Blei ki paidïapom ki Israel keiñ, ïa uba me la krenbeiñ.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ha kane ka sngi keiñ U Trai un aiti ïa me ha ka kti jong nga; te ngan shoh ïa me, bad ngan shim noh ïa ka khlieh jong me na me; bad ha kane ka sngi ngan ai noh ïa ki metïap ki paid ki Philistia ha ki sim ka suiñ, bad ha ki mrad khlaw ka khyndew; ba ka pyrthei baroh kan ïoh tip ba U Blei u don ha Israel.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Bad une u paidbah baroh un ïoh tip ba U Trai um pynim da ka waitlam lymne da u sum: namar ka jingïaleh thma ka long ka jong U Trai, bad un aiti noh ïa phi ha ka kti jong ngi.”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te haba uta u Philistia u la ïeng, bad ba u la wan hajan ban ïashem bad u Dabid, ynda kumta, u Dabid u la pynkloi, bad u la mareh sha uta u paidïapom ban ïashem bad uta u Philistia.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Bad u Dabid u la buh ïa la ka kti ha la ka pla, bad u la shim nangta ïa u maw, bad u la shat, bad la dei ïa uta u Philistia na ka shyllangmat; te uta u maw u la ngam shapoh ka shyllangmat jong u, te u la kyllon pyrkup slup ha ka khyndew.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la jop ïa uta u Philistia da ka jingshat maw bad da u maw, bad u la shoh ïa uta u Philistia, bad u la pynïap ïa u; la um don ka waitlam ruh ha ka kti u Dabid.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la mareh, bad u la ïeng halor uta u Philistia, bad u la shim ïa ka waitlam jong u, bad u la sei noh ïa ka na kata ka jingsop, bad u la pynïap khoit ïa u, bad u la khrai noh ïa ka khlieh jong u da ka. Te haba kita ki Philistia ki la ïohi ba u la ïap u riewradbah jong ki, ki la phet ïap noh.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Bad ki paidbah Israel bad Judah ki la ïeng, bad ki la risa, bad ki la beh ïa ki Philistia, haduh kaba poi ha Gath, bad haduh ki khyrdop ka Ekron keiñ. Te kita ki Philistia ki la kyllon ba la pynmynsaw ïa ki ha kata ka lynti sha Shaaraim, jin haduh Gath, bad haduh Ekron de.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Te ki khun Israel ki la wan phai noh na kaba beh ïa ki Philistia, bad ki la lute ïa ki ïingjaiñ jong ki.",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te u Dabid u la shim ïa ka khlieh uta u Philistia bad u la wallam ïa ka sha Jerusalem; hynrei, ïa kata ka jingkieng atiar jong u, u la buh ha la ka ïingjaiñ.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Te haba u Saul u la ïohi ïa u Dabid ba u da leit mih ban ïaleh bad uta u Philistia, u la kylli ïa u Abner u nongïalam u paidïapom, “Une u samla u khun jongno, ko Abner?” Te u Abner u la ïathuh, “Katba ka im ka mynsiem jong me, ko syiem, ngam tip.”",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Te uta u syiem u la ong, “To da kylli une u samla u long u khun jongno.”",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Te haba u Dabid u la wan phai noh na kaba pynïap ïa uta u Philistia, u Abner u la shim ïa u, bad u la ïalam ïa u ha khmat u Saul, te kata ka khlieh uta u Philistia ka la don ha ka kti jong u.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> Te u Saul u la kylli ïa u, “Me u khun jongno, ko samla?” Te u Dabid u la ïathuh, “Nga u khun u shakri jong me, u Jesse u nong Bethlehem.”"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda u la wai noh ban kren ha u Saul, u Jonathan bad u Dabid ki la ïa-ieit thep mynsiem, bad u Jonathan u la ieit ïa u kum la ka jong ka mynsiem.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Saul u la shim ïa u ha lade ha kata ka sngi, bad um shah shuh ba un leit phai noh sha ka ïing u kpa jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jonathan bad u Dabid ki la ïateh jutang, naba u la ieit ïa u kum la ka jong ka mynsiem.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Jonathan u la loit noh na lade ïa kata ka barandi kaba u kup, bad u la aiti ïa ka ha u Dabid, bad ïa la ki jaiñkup jaiñsem, jin haduh ïa la ka waitlam, bad ïa la ka ryntieh, bad ïa la ka jingpanpoh de.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Dabid u la leit shano shano kat sha kaba u Saul u la phah ïa u, bad u la ïaid leh sian ïa lade: bad u Saul u la buh ïa u halor ki paidïapom, bad u la long uba la sngewbha ïa u ha khmat kita ki paidbah baroh, bad ha khmat ki shakri u Saul ruh de.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba u Dabid u wan phai noh na kaba pynïap ïa uta u Philistia, ki kynthei ki la ïawan mih na ki nongbah ki Israel baroh, ki da ïarwai bad ki da ïashad, ban tan ïa u Saul syiem, bad ki kanjari, bad ka jingkmen, bad ki kynja jingtem.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te kita ki kynthei katba ki ïarwai ki la ïakren markylliang, bad ki la ïa-ong, “U Saul u la pynïap ïa la ki hajar, te u Dabid ïa la ki phew hajar.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Saul u la bitar lep, bad kane ka jingong ka la pynsngewsih ïa u; bad u la ong, “Ha u Dabid ki la ai phew hajar, te ha nga ki la ai tang ki hajar: sah sa aïu pat ba un ïoh, hynrei, sa tang ka jinglong syiem hi?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Saul u la khmih sian ïa u Dabid naduh kata ka sngi artet.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ha kaba lashai, ka la jia ba uta u mynsiem bymman uba na U Blei u la wan jur ha u Saul, bad u la ïathuhlypa hapdeng kata ka ïing; te u Dabid u la tem da la ka kti kumba mynshuwa: bad u sum u la don ha ka kti u Saul.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Saul u la sum ïa uta u sum; bad u la ong, “Ngan sum lyngba ïa u Dabid sha kata ka kynroh.” Te u Dabid u la kynriah noh ar sien na khmat jong u.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Saul u la sheptieng ïa u Dabid, namar ba U Trai u la don lem bad u, bad u la kiar noh na u Saul.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Namar kata, u Saul u la pynkynriah noh ïa u na u, bad u pynlong ïa u, u nongïalam halor shi hajar; te u la leit shabar bad u la wan shapoh ha shuwa uta u paidbah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Dabid u la ïaid leh sian ïa lade ha ki lynti jong u baroh; bad U Trai u la don lem bad u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad haba u Saul u la ïohi ba u la ïaid leh sian eh, u la sheptieng ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, ki Israel bad ki Judah baroh ki la ieit ïa u Dabid; namar ba u la leit shabar bad ba u la wan shapoh ha shuwa jong ki.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Saul u la ong ha u Dabid, “Ha khmih, ka khun nyngkong jong nga, ka Merab, ïa ka ngan ai kurim ha me: hynrei, tang ba men long uba shlur ïa nga, bad ba men ïaleh ïa ka jingïaleh thma U Trai.” Namar u Saul u la ong, “Ka kti jong nga kan ym long halor jong u, hynrei, to ka kti ki Philistia kan long halor jong u.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Saul, “Nga, nga long uei? bad ka jingim jong nga, lane ka ïing u kpa jong nga, ki ïalong aïu ha Israel, ba ngan ïoh long u pyrsa kurim u syiem?”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, ha kata ka por ha kaba la dei ban ai noh ïa ka Merab ka khun u Saul ha u Dabid, la ai kurim noh ïa ka pynban ha u Adriel u nong Meholath.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te ka Mikhal ka khun u Saul ka la ieit ïa u Dabid: bad ki la ïathuh ha u Saul, bad u la sngewbha ïa kata.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Saul u la ong, “Ngan ai ïa ka ha u, ba kan ïoh long ka jingriam ïa u, bad ba ka kti ki Philistia kan long pyrshah ïa u.” Kumta, u Saul u la ong ha u Dabid, “Ha kane ka sngi men ïoh long u pyrsa kurim jong nga sa shi sien pat.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Saul u la hukum ïa la ki shakri kumne, “To ïakren harieh bad u Dabid, da kaba ong, ‘Ha khmih, u syiem u sngewbha ïa me, bad ki shakri jong u baroh ki ieit ïa me: mynta te namar kata, to men long u pyrsa kurim u syiem.’ ”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad ki shakri u Saul ki la kren ïa kine ki ktien ha ki shkor u Dabid. Te u Dabid u la ong, “Phi ñiew sting mo ban long u pyrsa kurim u syiem, haba nga ruh u baduk, bad u bapoh?”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te kita ki shakri u Saul ki la ïathuh ha u, ki ong, “Kumne u la kren u Dabid.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Saul u la ong, “Kumne phin ong ha u Dabid, ‘U syiem um kwah hi ïa ka jingaiseng, hynrei, tang ban ïoh shispah tylli ki sher ki Philistia, ba yn pynhiar kput halor ki nongshun u syiem.’ ” Hynrei, u Saul u la thew khnang ban pynïap ïa u Dabid da ka kti ki Philistia.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te haba kita ki shakri jong u ki la ïathuh ha u Dabid ïa kine ki ktien, u Dabid u la sngewbha eh ban long u pyrsa kurim u syiem. Te ym pat biang ki sngi;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> bad u Dabid u la ïeng bad u la leit, ma u bad ki briew jong u, bad u la pynïap ïa arspah ngut ki Philistia; bad u Dabid u la wallam ïa ki sher jong ki, bad u la ai noh biang biang ïa ki ha u syiem, ba un ïoh long u pyrsa kurim u syiem. Te u Saul u la ai kurim noh ïa ka Mikhal ka khun jong u ha u.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u Saul u la ïohi bad u la tip ba U Trai u la don lem bad u Dabid; bad ka Mikhal ka khun u Saul ka la ieit ïa u.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Saul u la nang kham sheptieng pynban ïa u Dabid; bad u Saul u la long u nongshun u Dabid ha la ka sngi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ynda kumta, ki rangbah ki Philistia ki la leit mih: te katba ki leit mih, u Dabid u la ju kham leh sian ïa lade ban ïa ki shakri u Saul baroh; kumta la ñiewkor eh ïa ka nam jong u."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Saul u la kren ha u Jonathan u khun jong u, bad ha ki shakri jong u baroh, ba kin pynïap ïa u Dabid.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei, u Jonathan u khun u Saul u la ieit eh ïa u Dabid. Bad u Jonathan u la ïathuh ha u Dabid, u da ong, “U Saul u kpa jong nga u thew ban pynïap ïa me: namar kata te, nga kyrpad ïa me, to sumar ïa lade lashai mynstep, bad to sah ha ka jaka rieh, bad to buhrieh ïa lade:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> te ngan mih shabar bad ngan ïeng hajan u kpa jong nga ha kata ka lyngkha ha kaba me don, te ngan ïakren bad u kpa jong nga shaphang jong me; te katba nga tip, ngan ïathuh ha me.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad u Jonathan u la kren bha shaphang u Dabid ha u Saul u kpa jong u, bad la ong ha u, “To u syiem un ym leh pop ïa la u shakri, ïa u Dabid keiñ; namar um shym leh pop ma u ïa me, bad namar ba ki jingleh jong u ki long ki babha eh ïa me:",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> namar u la kheiñduh ïa la ka jingim, bad u la pynïap ïa uta u Philistia, bad U Trai u la pynlong ïa ka jinglait im bakhraw ïa ki Israel baroh; te me la ïohi ïa kata bad me la shadkmen; na ka balei te men leh pop ïa ka snam kaba lui lui, da kaba pynïap ïa u Dabid khlem daw?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u Saul u la shahshkor ïa ka ktien u Jonathan: bad u Saul u la smai, “Katba im U Trai, yn ym pynïap ïa u.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u Jonathan u la khot ïa u Dabid, bad u Jonathan u la ïathuh ha u ïa kine kiei kiei baroh. Bad u Jonathan u la ïalam ïa u Dabid sha u Saul, bad u la long ha khmat jong u, kumba mynhynnin mynshisngi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ka la don ka thma pat; bad u Dabid u la leit mih noh, bad u la ïaleh ïa ki Philistia, bad u la pynïap ïa ki da ka jingpynïap kaba khraw; te ki la phet ïap na khmat jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u mynsiem bymman uba na U Trai u la don ha u Saul, katba u la shong ha la ïing bad la u sum ha la ka kti: te u Dabid u la tem da la ka kti.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Saul u la pyrshang ban sum lyngba ïa u Dabid haduh kata ka kynroh da uta u sum; hynrei, u la kynriah noh na khmat u Saul, u te u la sum ïa uta u sum sha kata ka kynroh: bad u Dabid u la phet ïap bad u la lait im ha kata ka miet.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u Saul u la phah briew sha ka ïing u Dabid, ban ap thap ïa u, bad ban pynïap ïa u mynstep; te ka Mikhal ka tnga jong u, ka la ïathuh ha u, ka da ong, “Lada men ym pynim ïa la ka jingim mynta mynmiet, lashai mynstep yn pynïap ïa me.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta, ka Mikhal ka la pynhiar arsut ïa u Dabid na ka jingkhang ïit: te u la leit, bad u la phet ïap, bad u la lait.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ka Mikhal ka la shim ïa ki teraph, bad ka la buh ïa ki ha kata ka jingthiah, bad ka la buh ka syngkhlieh kaba na u 'ñiuh blang ha ka khlieh jong ka, bad ka la tap ïa ka da ki jaiñ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u Saul u la phah briew ban kem ïa u Dabid, ka la ong, “U pang”.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Saul u la phah ïa kita ki briew ban jngoh ïa u Dabid, u da ong, “Wallam noh artet ïa u sha nga ha la ka jingthiah, ba ngan ïoh pynïap ïa u.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba kita ki briew ki la poi, ha khmih, kita ki teraph pleng ha kata ka jingthiah, bad ka syngkhlieh kaba na u 'ñiuh blang ha ka khlieh jong ka.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Saul u la ong ha ka Mikhal, “Balei pha la shukor ïa nga kumne, bad ba pha la pyllait noh ïa u nongshun jong nga, ba un ïohlait?” Te ka Mikhal ka la ïathuh ha u Saul, “U la ong ha nga, ‘To pyllait noh ïa nga; ngan pynïap balei ïa pha?’ ”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la phet ïap, bad u la lait, bad u la wan poi ha u Samuel sha Ramah, bad u la ïathuh ha u ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba u la leh u Saul ha u. Te ma u bad u Samuel ki la leit bad ki la ïashong ha Naioth.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u Saul, da kaba ong, “Ha khmih, u Dabid u ha Naioth ha Ramah.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Saul u la phah briew ban kem ïa u Dabid: te haba kita ki la ïohi ïa uta u paidbah ki nongïathuhlypa ba ki ïathuhlypa, bad ba u Samuel u la ïeng kum u rangbah jong ki, U Mynsiem U Blei u la wan ha kita ki briew jong u Saul, ba kumta ki hi ruh ki la ïathuhlypa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba la ïathuh ïa kane ha u Saul, u la phah ïa kiwei pat ki briew, te kita ruh ki la ïathuhlypa. Te u Saul u la phah briew pat ka balai sien, kita ruh ki la ïathuhlypa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, u hi ruh u la leit sha Ramah, bad u la wan poi ha kata ka pukri ka bakhraw kaba ha Sekhu: bad u la kylli bad u la ong, “U Samuel bad u Dabid ki ha-ei?” Te uwei u la ïathuh, “Ha khmih, ki don ha Naioth ha Ramah.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u la leit sha Naioth ha Ramah: bad U Mynsiem U Blei u la wan ha u ruh, te u la nang leit, bad u la ïathuhlypa, haduh ba u la poi sha Naioth ha Ramah.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad u ruh u la loit noh ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u la ïathuhlypa ruh ha khmat u Samuel, bad u la thiah lyngkhuit baroh kata ka sngi bad baroh kata ka miet. Namar kata, ki la ju ong, “U Saul ruh pleng u don hapdeng ki nongïathuhlypa?”"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Dabid u la phet noh na Naioth kaba ha Ramah, bad u la wan bad u la ong ha khmat u Jonathan, “Hato nga la leh aïu? Kaei ka jingbymman jong nga? Bad kaei ka pop jong nga ha khmat u kpa jong me, ba u wad kumne ïa ka mynsiem jong nga?”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la ong ha u, “Kam long kumta, em; men ym ïap: ha khmih, u kpa jong nga un ym leh ei ei ruh lymne ka bakhraw lymne ka barit khlem da ïathuh ha nga: te u kpa jong nga un buhrieh ïa kane na nga balei? kam long kumta.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Dabid u la smai de, bad u la ong, “U kpa jong me u tip bha ba nga la shem kaba sngewbha ha khmat jong me; bad u ong, ‘Wat ai ba u Jonathan un ïoh tip ïa kane, ïoh pynsngewsih ïa u;’ da shisha katba im U Trai, bad katba im ka mynsiem jong me ruh, ka don tang kum shi sien-jam hapdeng jong nga bad ka jingïap.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jonathan u la ong ha u Dabid, “Ïa kano kano kaba kwah ka mynsiem jong me, ïa kata ngan leh na ka bynta jong me.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Jonathan, “Ha khmih, lashai long u bnai u bathymmai, te da lei lei nga dei ban shong bam bad u syiem: hynrei, to shah ba ngan leit, ngan rieh ïa lade ha lyngkha, haduh ka sngi ka balai ynda janmiet.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Lada u kpa jong me un kylli shaphang jong nga, me te men ong, ‘U Dabid u la pan khnang na nga ba un ïoh leit jang jang sha Bethlehem ka shnong jong u: naba ka jingkñia kaba shi snem shi snem ka don hangta ïa ki kur baroh.’",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Lada un ong kumne, ‘To ñiuma’; u shakri jong me un ïoh suk: hynrei, lada un bitar lep, kumta to tip ba u la thew khnang ïa ka basniew.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Namar kata, to leh isynei ïa la u shakri; naba me la ïalam ïa la u shakri lem bad me ha ka jutang U Trai: hynrei, lada don ei ei ka basniew ha nga, to pynïap ma me ïa nga; namar ïa ka ban lei ba men ïalam ïa nga sha u kpa jong me?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Jonathan u la ong, “Wat ai kan long kumta ïa me haba da lei lei: namar lada nga la tip ei ei ba u kpa jong nga u la thew ïa ka basniew ha me, balei ngan ym ïathuh ïa me?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Jonathan, “Uei u ban ïathuh ha nga, lada u kpa jong me un phai ktien ïa me da kaba eh?”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Jonathan u la ong ha u Dabid, “Ale, ngin ïaleit kai sha lyngkha.” Te ki la ïaleit kai baroh ar ngut sha lyngkha.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Jonathan u la ong ha u Dabid, “U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, un long sakhi: ynda nga la tynjuh ïa la u kpa kum ha kane ka por lashai, lane lashisngi, te ha khmih, lada kan long ka babha ïa u Dabid, nga ngan ym phah ïathuh ïa kata ha me?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U Trai un leh kumta, bad tam ruh, ïa u Jonathan, lada u kpa jong nga un ibit ban pynsniew ïa me, bad ba ngan ym ïathuh ïa me bad pyllait noh ïa me, ba men ïoh leit ha kaba suk: te U Trai to un long lem bad me, kumba u la long bad u kpa jong nga.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te men leh ïa ka jingisynei U Trai ïa nga ym tang katba nga dang im ma nga, ba kumta hi ngan ym ïap:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> hynrei ruh, wat pynkut noh ïa la ka jingisynei na ka ïing jong nga lano lano ruh: em, lymne ynda U Trai u la pynjot noh ïa ki nongshun u Dabid uwei pa uwei baroh na khmat ka pyrthei.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kumta, u Jonathan u la pynlong ka jutang bad ka ïing u Dabid, da kaba ong, “To U Trai un dawa ïa kane na ka kti ki nongshun u Dabid.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Jonathan u la pynsmai pat ïa u Dabid ruh, namar ka jingieit jong u ïa u: naba u la ieit ïa u kumjuh kumba u la ieit ïa la ka jong ka mynsiem.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, u Jonathan u la ong ha u Dabid, “Lashai long u bnai u bathymmai: te yn kylli shaphang jong me, namar kan long suda ka jaka shong jong me.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ynda me la sah lai sngi, men leit hiar kloi, bad to wan sha kata ka jaka ha kaba me la rieh mynba la long kata kawei ka kam, bad to sah hajan u maw Esel.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te nga ruh ngan siat lai tylli ki khnam na syndah jong u, kum ban siat nishan.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad, ha khmih, ngan phah ïa u samla uwei, da kaba ong, ‘Khie leit, da wad ïa kita ki khnam.’ Lada ngan ong ha uta u samla, ‘Ha khmih, kita ki khnam ki shaphang shane na me: to shim ïa ki, ale noh’; namar men ïoh suk bad men ym lei lei, katba im U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, lada ngan ong kumne ha uta u samla, ‘Ha khmih, kita ki khnam ki sha shuwa jong me:’ to men leit noh; naba U Trai u la phah noh ïa me.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te shaphang kata ka kam kaba ma me bad nga ngi la ïakren, ha khmih, U Trai u long hapdeng jong me bad jong nga junom.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la rieh ïa lade ha kata ka lyngkha: te haba la poi u bnai u bathymmai, u syiem u la shong ban bam.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u syiem u la shong ha la ka jaka shong, kumba ha kiwei pat ki por, kata, ha ka jaka shong hajan ka kynroh; te u Jonathan u la ïeng, bad u Abner u la shong hajan u Saul: hynrei, ka jaka u Dabid ka la long suda.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> La kumta ruh, u Saul um shym ong ei ei ha kata ka sngi: namar u la mut, “Ade la jia ei ei ha u, um long khuid: shisha um khuid keiñ.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ha kaba lashai u bnai u bathymmai, ka sngi ka ba-ar keiñ, ka jaka u Dabid ka la long suda; bad u Saul u la ong ha u Jonathan u khun jong u, “Balei ba u khun u Jesse um shym wan sha ka jingbam mynhynnin, bad mynta ruh?”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te u Jonathan u la ïathuh ha u Saul, “U Dabid u la kyrpad eh na nga ba un ïoh leit sha Bethlehem:",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad u la ong, ‘Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ba ngan leit; namar ka ïing jong ngi ka don ka jingkñia ha shnong; bad u hynmen jong nga u la hukum ïa nga ba ngan don hangta: te mynta, lada nga la shem kaba sngewbha ha khmat jong me, nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ba ngan leit, ba ngan ïoh jngoh ïa la ki hynmen.’ Namar kata, um shym wan sha ka miej u syiem.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ynda kumta, ka jingbitar u Saul ka la meh lep ïa u Jonathan, bad u la ong ha u, “Me u khun jong kata ka bakiat bad bamutlop, nga ngam tip ba me la jied ïa une u khun u Jesse ban long ka jingjahburom ïa me, bad ban long ka jinglehrain ïa ka jinglyngkhuit ka kmie jong me?",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Namar katba une u khun u Jesse u dang im ha kane ka pyrthei, yn ym pynskhem ïa me, lymne ïa ka hima jong me. Namar kata te, to phah bad wallam ïa u sha nga, namar un ïap shisha keiñ.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u Jonathan u la ïathuh ha u Saul u kpa jong u, bad u la ong ha u, “Un ïap namar balei? u la leh aïu?”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u Saul u la sum ïa u sum sha u ban sum ïa u: na kane u Jonathan u la tip ba u kpa jong u, u la thew skhem ban pynïap ïa u Dabid.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Kumta, u Jonathan u la ïeng na kata ka miej da kaba bitar lep, bad um shym bam jingbam ha kata ka sngi ka ba-ar jong uta u bnai: namar u la sngewsih na ka bynta u Dabid, namar ba u kpa jong u, u la pynjahburom ïa u.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Mynstep te, u Jonathan u la leit sha kata ka lyngkha hamar kata ka por ba la ïabuh bad u Dabid, bad u khynnah u barit lem bad u.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Bad u la ong ha uta u khynnah jong u, “To mareh, bad wad ïa ki khnam kiba nga siat.” Te katba uta u khynnah u mareh, u ruh u la siat pynbud ïa u khnam sha shuwa jong u.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te haba uta u khynnah u la poi sha kata ka jaka ha kaba la don uta u khnam ba la siat u Jonathan, u Jonathan u la pyrta nadien uta u khynnah, bad u la ong, “Uto u khnam um long sha shuwa jong me?”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad u Jonathan u la pyrta nadien uta u khynnah, “Pynstet, pynkloi, wat da ap.” Bad uta u khynnah u Jonathan u la khar ïa kita ki khnam, bad u la wan phai sha la u kynrad.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te uta u khynnah um shym tip ei ei: hynrei, tang u Jonathan hi bad u Dabid ki la tip ïa kata ka kam.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te u Jonathan u la ai ïa kita ki atiar jong u ha uta u khynnah jong u, bad u la ong ha u, “Khie leit lam sha shnong.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te tang shu leit noh uta u khynnah, u Dabid u la mih noh na shaphang shathie, bad u la hap dem la ka khmat sha ka khyndew, bad u la dem nguh lai sien: bad ki la ïadoh paralok hi, bad ki la ïaïam lem, te u la kham jur u Dabid.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad u Jonathan u la ong ha u Dabid, “To khie leit ha kaba suk, namar ngi la ïasmai baroh ar ngut ha ka kyrteng U Trai, da kaba ong, ‘To U Trai un long hapdeng jong nga bad jong me, bad hapdeng u symbai jong nga bad u symbai jong me, junom.’ ” U, te, u la ïeng bad u la leit noh: bad u Jonathan u la leit sha shnong."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la leit poi sha Nob ha u Ahimelekh u lyngdoh: te u Ahimelekh u la wan tan ïa u Dabid da kaba sheptieng, bad u la ong ha u, “Balei ba me tang weibriew, bad bymdon mano mano ruh lem bad me?”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Ahimelekh u lyngdoh, “U syiem u la hukum ïa nga shaphang kano kano ka kam, bad u la ong ha nga, ‘Wat ai ba uno uno ruh un tip ei ei shaphang kata ka kam ïa kaba nga la phah ïa me, bad kaba nga la hukum ïa me’: te ïa ki samla nga la phah noh hangtai.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te me don aïu ha la ka kti? to ai ïa nga san tylli ki kpu ha ka kti jong nga, lane ïa kaei kaei katba don.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te uta u lyngdoh u la ïathuh ha u Dabid, bad u la ong, “Ym don kpu u bymkyntang ha ka kti jong nga, hynrei, don u kpu bakyntang; tang lada kita ki samla ki la kyndiah na ki kynthei.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Dabid u la ïathuh ha uta u lyngdoh, bad u la ong ha u, “Da shisha la pynkyndiah ïa ngi na ki kynthei la kumba lai sngi: naduh ba nga la mih noh, ki pliang jong kine ki samla ki la long ki bakhuid, bad u kpu hi ruh u syriem kum u bymkyntang, haba la don da uwei pat ba la pynkyntang ha u khiew ha kane ka sngi.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, uta u lyngdoh u la ai ha u ïa u kpu bakyntang: namar ym shym don kpu hangta, hynrei, tang uta u 'pu pyni, ïa uba la sei noh na khmat U Trai, ba yn ïoh buh da u kpu bashit ha ka sngi ba la lah sei noh ïa uta keiñ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ha kata ka sngi la don uwei na ki shakri u Saul, ïa uba la pynsah ha khmat U Trai: uba kyrteng “u Doeg” u nong Edom, uba kham rangbah na ki nongsumar jingri ba dei ha u Saul.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Ahimelekh, “Don ne em hangne ha ka kti jong me u sum lane ka waitlam? namar ngam shym wallam bad nga lymne ïa la ka waitlam lymne ïa la ki atiar, naba ka kam u syiem ka kyrkieh eh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te uta u lyngdoh u la ong, “Kata ka waitlam u Goliath u nong Philistia, ïa uba me la pynïap ma me ha ka them Elah, ha khmih, ka don hangne ha lyndet kata ka ephod ba la sop ha ka jaiñ: lada men shim ïa kata, to shim: namar ym don kawei pat, sa tang kata hi.” Bad u Dabid u la ong, “Kat kata ym ju don shuh; to ai ïa ka ha nga.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ïeng, bad u la phet noh ha kata ka sngi ba u sheptieng ïa u Saul, bad u la leit sha u Akhish u syiem ka Gath.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki shakri u Akhish ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Une um long u Dabid u syiem jong kata ka ri? ym long ïa une ruh ba ki la ïarwai markylliang ha kita ki jingshad, ki da ong, “ ‘U Saul u la pynïap ïa la ki hajar, te u Dabid ïa la ki phew hajar?’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u Dabid u la buh ïa kita ki ktien ha la ka dohnud, bad u la sheptieng eh ïa u Akhish u syiem ka Gath.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u la pynbakla ïa la ka jingleh ha khmat jong ki, bad u la leh mynleh lamwir ïa lade ha ki kti jong ki, bad u la trud ha ki jingkhang jong kata ka khyrdop, bad u pynjaw dud umbiah ha u 'ñiuh tmoh jong u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kumta te u Akhish u la ong ha la ki shakri, “Ha khmih, phi ïohi ba une u briew uba lamwir; balei te phi la wallam noh ïa u sha nga?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nga kyrduh kiba lamwir mo, ba phi la wallam ïa une ban leh lamwir ha khmat jong nga? kum une kumno un ïoh wan ha ïing jong nga?”"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> U Dabid te, namar kata, u la leit noh nangta, bad u la phet noh sha ka krem Adullam: te haba ki hynmen jong u bad baroh ka ïing u kpa jong u ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la ïaleit hiar noh shato sha u.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad uwei uwei baroh uba ha ka jynjar, bad uwei uwei baroh uba dap ram, bad uwei uwei baroh uba la kthang la ka mynsiem, ki la ïalum lang sha u; te u la long rangbah halor jong ki: te ki la don hangta lem bad u kumba sawspah ki rangbah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Dabid u la leit noh nangta sha Mispeh ri Moab: bad u la ong ha u syiem ka Moab, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa u kpa jong nga bad ïa ka kmie jong nga ban wan shong bad phi, tad ynda ngan ïoh tip U Blei un leh kumno ïa nga.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u la ïalam ïa ki ha khmat u syiem ka Moab: bad ki la shong lem bad u baroh ki sngi ba u Dabid u la don ha kata ka kut.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Gad u nongïathuhlypa u la ong ha u Dabid, “Wat sah shuh ha kane ka kut; to mih noh, bad leit noh sha ka ri Judah.” Kumta, u Dabid u la mih noh, bad u la leit poi sha ka khlaw Hareth.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Saul u la ïohsngew ba la ïoh tip shaphang u Dabid, bad kita ki briew kiba bad u: te u Saul u la shong ha Gibeah hapoh uwei u dieng ha Ramah, u da don ruh u sum ha la ka kti, bad ki shakri jong u baroh ki da ïeng baroh sawdong ïa u:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ynda kumta, u Saul u la ong ha la ki shakri kiba ïeng baroh sawdong ïa u, “To sngap mynta, phi ki Benjamin; une u khun u Jesse un ai mo ha uwei uwei baroh na phi da ki lyngkha bad ki brisoh Waiñ, un pynlong ne em ïa phi baroh ki nongïalam halor ki hajar, bad ki nongïalam halor ki spah;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ba phi baroh phi la ïabuit lem pyrshah ïa nga, bad ba ym don u ban ïathuh ha nga haba u khun jong nga u la ïateh jutang bad une u khun u Jesse, bad ba ym don uno uno na phi uba sngewsih na ka bynta jong nga, lymne uba ïathuh ha nga ba u khun jong nga u la pynkhih ïa u shakri jong nga, ban ap thap, kumba ha kane ka sngi?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, uta u Doeg u nong Edom, ïa uba la buh halor ki shakri u Saul, u la ïathuh, bad u la ong, “Nga la ïohi ïa u khun u Jesse ba u wan sha Nob, ha u Ahimelekh u khun u Ahitub.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad u la ïakylli na U Trai na ka bynta jong u, bad u la ai jingbam ïa u, bad u la ai ha u ïa kata ka waitlam u Goliath u nong Philistia.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, u syiem u la phah khot ïa u Ahimelekh u lyngdoh, u khun u Ahitub, bad ïa baroh ka ïing u kpa jong u, kita ki lyngdoh kiba ha Nob keiñ: bad ki la ïawan baroh ha u syiem.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> U Saul te u la ong, “To sngap mynta, me u khun u Ahitub.” U ruh u la ong, “Nga hangne, ko kynrad.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Saul u la ong ha u, “Na ka balei phi la ïashet buit lem pyrshah ïa nga, ma me bad u khun u Jesse, ha kaba me la ai kpu ïa u, bad ka waitlam, bad ba me la ïakylli jingkylli na U Blei na ka bynta jong u, ba kumta un ïeng ïaleh ïa nga, ban ap thap, kumba ha kane ka sngi?”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Ahimelekh u la ïathuh ha u syiem, bad u la ong, “Napdeng ki shakri jong me baroh, uei uba bit ban shaniah kat u Dabid, uba long ruh u pyrsa kurim u syiem, bad uba leit ha ka hukum jong me, bad uba donburom ha ka ïing jong me?",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hato dei tang ha kata ka sngi ba nga la sdang ban ïakylli ïa U Blei na ka bynta jong u? kam long kumta, em: wat ai ba u syiem un pynkit ei ei halor u shakri jong u, lymne halor uno uno ruh na ka ïing u kpa jong nga: naba u shakri jong me um tip ei ei na kane baroh, lymne kaba khyndiat lymne shibun.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> U syiem te u la ong, “Ko Ahimelekh, da kaba ïap men ïap shisha, ma me, bad baroh ka ïing u kpa jong me.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u syiem u la ong ha kita ki nongphet kiba ïeng sawdong ïa u, “To phai, bad pynïap ïa ki lyngdoh jong U Trai: naba ka kti jong ki ruh ka don lem bad u Dabid, bad ba haba ki la tip ba u la phet noh, kim shym ïathuh ha nga.” Hynrei, ki shakri u syiem kim treh ban rah ïa la ka kti ban pynïap ïa ki lyngdoh jong U Trai.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te u syiem u la ong ha u Doeg, “To phai ma me, to pynïap ïa kita ki lyngdoh.” Bad u Doeg u nong Edom u la phai, bad u la tur ha kita ki lyngdoh, bad u la pynïap ha kata ka sngi phraphew san ngut ki rangbah kiba ju phong ïa ka ephod linen.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ïa ka Nob ruh, kaba ka shnong kita ki lyngdoh, u la pynïap da ka syrti waitlam, ïa ki rangbah bad ïa ki kynthei, ïa ki khynnah bad ïa ki khunlung ba dang buiñ, ïa ki masi bad ïa ki kadda bad ïa ki langbrot, da ka syrti waitlam.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Uwei te na ki khun shynrang u Ahimelekh u khun u Ahitub, uba kyrteng “u Abiathar”, u la lait im bad u la phet ïap hadien u Dabid.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Abiathar u la ïathuh ha u Dabid ba u Saul u la pynïap ïa ki lyngdoh jong U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Abiathar, “Nga la tip ha kata ka sngi, haba uta u Doeg u nong Edom u la don hangta, ba un ym pep ban ïathuh ha u Saul: nga la pynwan ma nga ïa ka jingïap ha kita ki briew baroh kiba dei ha ka ïing u kpa jong me.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> To sah ma me bad nga, wat sheptieng; naba uta uba wad ïa ka jingim jong nga u wad ïa ka jingim jong me ruh: hynrei, bad nga men ïoh ka jingïada.”"
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïathuh ha u Dabid, ki ïa-ong, “Ha khmih, ki Philistia ki ïaleh thma ïa ka Keilah, bad ki ïalute ïa ki kyntem.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Namar kata, u Dabid u la kylli na U Trai, u da ong, “Ngan leit ne em, bad ngan pom ïa kine ki Philistia?” Te U Trai u la ïathuh ha u Dabid, “Khie leit, bad pom ïa ki Philistia, bad pyllait im ïa ka Keilah.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki rangbah u Dabid ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Ha khmih, ngi ïasheptieng wat hangne ha Judah: sa katno tam te lei lei lada ngin leit sha Keilah ban ïaleh ïa ki paidïapom ki Philistia?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la kylli pat na U Trai. Bad U Trai u la ïathuh ha u bad u la ong, “To ïeng, to leit hiar sha Keilah; namar ngan sa aiti ïa ki Philistia ha ka kti jong me.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, u Dabid bad ki rangbah jong u ki la ïaleit sha Keilah, bad u la ïaleh thma ïa ki Philistia, bad u la knieh noh ïa ki masi jong ki, bad u la pom ïa ki da ka jingpynïap kaba khraw. Kumta u Dabid u la pyllait im ïa ki nong Keilah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ka la long te, haba u Abiathar u khun u Ahimelekh u la phet ïap sha u Dabid ha Keilah, ba u la wallam ruh ïa ka ephod ha la ka kti.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u Saul ba u Dabid u la wan poi sha Keilah. Bad u Saul u la ong, “U Blei u la aiti ïa u ha ka kti jong nga: naba la set kut ïa u, haba u la rung shapoh ka shnong kaba don ki khyrdop bad ki dieng jingkhang.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Saul u la lum khar paid ban ïaleh thma, ban leit hiar sha Keilah, ban ker kut ïa u Dabid bad ïa ki rangbah jong u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Dabid u la tip ba u Saul u la shetbuit sniew pyrshah ïa u; bad u la ong ha u Abiathar u lyngdoh, “To wallam shane ïa kata ka ephod.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la ong, “A Trai, U Blei ki Israel, u shakri jong me u la ïohsngew shisha ba u Saul u thew ban wan sha Keilah, ïa ka ban pynjot noh ïa ka shnong namar jong nga.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kine ki rangbah Keilah kin aiti noh ne em ïa nga ha ka kti jong u? bad un wan hiar ne em u Saul, kumba u la ïohsngew u shakri jong me? A Trai, U Blei ki Israel, nga kyrpad ïa me, to ïathuh ha la u shakri.” Te U Trai u la ïathuh, “Un wan hiar keiñ.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la kylli, “Kine ki rangbah Keilah kin aiti noh ne em ïa nga bad ïa ki rangbah jong nga ha ka kti u Saul?” Te U Trai u la ïathuh, “Kin aiti noh keiñ.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid bad u paidbah jong u, kumba hynriewspah ngut, ki la ïeng bad ki la leit noh na Keilah, bad ki la leit kylleng kat sha kaba ki lah. Te la ïathuh ha u Saul ba u Dabid u la phet noh na Keilah; u ruh u la pep ban leit mih noh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te u Dabid u la shong ha ka ri khlaw ha ki kut, bad u la shong sah ha ri lum ha ka ri khlaw Siph. Te u Saul u la wad ïa u ha la ka sngi, hynrei, U Blei um shym la aiti noh ïa u ha ka kti jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Dabid u la ïohi ba u Saul u la mih noh khnang ban wad ïa ka jingim jong u: te u Dabid u la don ha ri khlaw Siph ha ka 'law lynnong.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u Jonathan u khun u Saul u la ïeng, bad u la leit sha u Dabid ha kata ka 'law lynnong; bad u la kyrshan bor ïa ka kti jong u ha U Blei.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la ong ha u, “Wat sheptieng: naba ka kti u Saul u kpa jong nga kan ym ïoh kem ïa me; te men ïoh synshar halor ki Israel; bad nga ruh ngan long uba kham hajan ïa me; bad u Saul u kpa jong nga u tip ïa kata.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ki baroh ar ngut ki la ïateh ka jutang ha khmat U Trai: te u Dabid u la shong sah ha kata ka 'law lynnong, bad u Jonathan u la leit noh sha la ïing.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ynda kumta, ki Siph ki la leit kiew sha u Saul ha Gibeah, ki da ong, “U Dabid um buhrieh ïa lade bad ngi ha ki kut ha ka 'law lynnong ha i lum rit Hakhilah, iba shaphang shathie na Jeshimon?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Mynta te, ko syiem, to da wan hiar, katba kum ka jingkwah ka dohnud jong me baroh ban wan hiar; te kan long ha ngi keiñ ban aiti noh ïa u ha ka kti u syiem.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad u Saul u la ong, “To long phi ïa kiba la kyrkhu na U Trai; namar phi la leh isynei ïa nga.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nga kyrpad ïa phi, to leit khreh bha, bad to tip skhem bad khmih bniah ïa ka jaka jong u ha kaba u shait ïaid, bad uei ba la ïohi ïa u hangta: naba ki ïathuh ha nga ba u leh sian shikatdei.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> To khmih te namar kata, bad to tip bha ïa kita ki jaka rieh baroh ha kiba u rieh, bad to wan phai pat sha nga khnang, te ngan ïaleit lem bad phi: bad lada u don ha kane ka ri, ngan wad ïa u kylleng ha ki hajar Judah baroh.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te ki la ïeng, bad ki la leit sha Siph ha shuwa u Saul: hynrei, u Dabid bad u paidbah jong u ki la don ha ri khlaw Maon, ha kata ka pynthor kaba shaphang shathie na Jeshimon.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> U Saul ruh bad u paidbah jong u ki la leit wad ïa u. Te la ïathuh ha u Dabid: namar kata, u la leit hiar ha uta u mawsiang, bad u la shong ha kata ka ri khlaw Maon. Bad haba u Saul u la ïohsngew ïa kata, u la beh nadien u Dabid ha kata ka ri khlaw Maon.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te u Saul u la leit na kawei ka liang uta u lum, bad u Dabid bad u paidbah jong u na kawei pat ka liang uta u lum: bad u Dabid u la pynkloi ban leit noh ba u sheptieng ïa u Saul; namar u Saul bad u paidbah jong u ki la ker tawiar ïa u Dabid bad ïa u paidbah jong u ban kem ïa ki.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, u nongkit-ktien u la wan ha u Saul, u da ong, “To pynkloi, bad to wan noh; naba ki Philistia ki la wan hiar thma ha ka ri.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Kumta, u Saul u la leit phai noh na kaba beh nadien u Dabid, bad u la leit ïaleh ïa ki Philistia: namar kata, ki la khot kyrteng ïa kata ka jaka “Sela-hammah-lekoth.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad u Dabid u la leit kiew nangta, bad u la shong ha ki kut ha En-gedi."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba u Saul u la wan phai na kaba beh ïa ki Philistia, la ïathuh ha u, da kaba ong, “Ha khmih u Dabid u ha ri khlaw En-gedi.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda kumta, u Saul u la shim lai hajar ki rangbah ba la kynsai na ki Israel baroh, bad u la leit wad ïa u Dabid bad ïa u paidbah jong u halor ki mawsiang ki 'lang khlaw.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ha lynti u la wan poi ha ki jingker ki langbrot, ha kaba la don ka krem; bad u Saul u la leit bsut ïa ka ban leit khyndew. Te u Dabid bad u paidbah jong u ki la ïashong rieh ha kaba kham shapoh kata ka krem;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki rangbah u Dabid ki la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, kane hi ka sngi ba U Trai u la ong ha me shaphang jong ka, ‘Ha khmih, ngan aiti ïa u nongshun jong me ha ka kti jong me, ba men ïoh leh ïa u katba me ibit.’ ” Te u Dabid u la ïeng, bad u la ot noh ha kaba rieh ïa ka rmiang kata ka barandi kaba ha u Saul.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hadien kata, ka dohnud u Dabid ka la dung ïa u, namar ba u la ot noh ïa ka rmiang barandi u Saul.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad u la ïathuh ïa la ki rangbah, “To U Trai un khang ba ngan leh ïa kane ïa la u kynrad, ïa uba la sleh jong U Trai, kat ban rah ïa la ka kti pyrshah ïa u, haba u long ïa uba la sleh jong U Trai.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la khang ïa la ki rangbah da kine ki ktien, bad um shym shah ïa ki ban ïeng pyrshah ïa u Saul. Te u Saul u la ïeng ban mih noh na kata ka krem, bad u la leit noh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hadien kata, u Dabid ruh u la ïeng, bad u la mih noh na kata ka krem, bad u la pyrta nadien u Saul, u da ong, “Ko syiem kynrad jong nga.” Te haba u Saul u la kyrtiang, u Dabid u la dem ïa la ka khmat haduh khyndew, bad u la dem ngon.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha u Saul, “Balei ba me sngap ïa ki ktien ki briew kiba ong, ‘Ha khmih, u Dabid u thew ïa ka basniew ïa me?’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ha khmih, ha kane ka sngi ki khmat jong me ki la ïohi ba U Trai u la aiti ïa me ha ka kti jong nga ha kane ka sngi ha kata ka krem: bad don kiba la ong ïa nga ban pynïap ïa me: hynrei, nga la pyllait im ïa me; bad nga la ong, ‘Ngan ym rah ïa la ka kti pyrshah ïa la u kynrad; namar u long ïa uba la sleh jong U Trai.’",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad nalor kata ruh, to khmih, ko kpa jong nga, shisha, to khmih ïa ka rmiang ka barandi jong me ha ka kti jong nga; namar na kaba nga la ot noh ïa ka rmiang ka barandi jong me, khlem da pynïap ïa me, to tip keiñ bad to khmih ba ha ka kti jong nga ym don ka jingbymman lymne ka jingsniew, bad ba ngam shym la leh pop ïa me, pynban, ma me, me beh mrad ïa ka mynsiem jong nga khnang ban kem ïa ka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> To U Trai un bishar hapdeng jong nga bad jong me, bad to U Trai un pynhiar kput ïa nga halor jong me: hynrei, ka kti jong nga kan ym long halor jong me.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Kumta ka ong ka ktien ki tymmen, ‘Na u bymman ka mih ka bymman:’ hynrei, ka kti jong nga kan ym long halor jong me.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hadien jongno u la wan mih u syiem ki Israel? Hadien jongno me beh? Hadien u ksew baïap, hadien u thyllah keiñ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Namar kata, to U Trai un long nongbishar, bad to un bishar hapdeng jong nga bad jong me, to un khmih ruh, bad un ïasaid ïa ka hok jong nga, bad pyllait ïa nga na ka kti jong me.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba u Dabid u la wai noh ban kren ïa kine ki ktien ha u Saul, u Saul u la ong, “Kane ka long ka jingsawa ktien jong me, ko Dabid u khun jong nga?” Bad u Saul u la pynjam ïa la ka ktien, bad u la ïam.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u la ong ruh ha u Dabid, “Me kham hok ma me ban ïa nga: naba ma me, me la ai ïa nga da ka babha, nga te nga ai ïa me da ka basniew.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad ha kane ka sngi me la pyni ba me la leh ïa ka babha ïa nga: namar haba U Trai u la aiti ïa nga ha ka kti jong me, ma me pynban mem shym la pynïap ïa nga.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar lada u briew un da shem ïa la u nongshun, un pyllait noh ïa u ha kaba suk? namar kata, to U Trai un ai ïa me da ka babha na ka bynta kata kaba me la leh ïa nga ha kane ka sngi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te mynta, ha khmih, nga tip skhem ba men long syiem shisha, bad ba yn pynskhem ïa ka hima Israel ha ka kti jong me.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Mynta te, to smai ha nga da U Trai, ba men ym ot noh ïa u symbai jong nga hadien jong nga, bad ba men ym pynduh ïa ka kyrteng jong nga na ka ïing u kpa jong nga.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Dabid u la smai ha u Saul. Bad u Saul u la leit sha la ïing; hynrei, u Dabid bad u paidbah jong u ki la leit kiew sha kata ka kut."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Samuel u la ïap noh; bad ki Israel baroh ki la ïalum lang, bad ki la ïambriew ïa u, bad ki la tep ïa u ha ka ïing jong u ha Ramah. Bad u Dabid u la ïeng, bad u la leit hiar sha ri khlaw Paran.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te la don uwei u briew ha Maon, uba la don la ki spah jong u ha Karmel; te uta u briew u la khraw bor eh, bad u la don lai hajar ki langbrot, bad shi hajar ki blang: te u la dang ot shñiuh ïa la ki langbrot ha Karmel.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ka kyrteng uta u briew ka la long “u Nabal”; bad ka kyrteng ka tnga jong u “ka Abigail”: te kata ka briew ka la long kaba nang kaba sian, bad kaba bhabriew de: hynrei, uta u briew u la long uba eh runar, bad uba bymman ka jingleh jong u; bad u la long na ka ïing u Kaleb.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Dabid u la ïohsngew ha kata ka ri khlaw ba u Nabal u dang ot shñiuh ïa la ki langbrot.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Dabid u la phah shiphew ngut ki samla, bad u Dabid u la ong ha kita ki samla, “Khie leit kiew sha Karmel bad leit ha u Nabal, bad to khublei ïa u ha ka kyrteng jong nga:",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad kumne phin ong ha uta uba im suk, ‘To long ka jingsuk ïa me, bad ka jingsuk ha ka ïing jong me, bad ka jingsuk ha kiei kiei baroh ki jong me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te mynta nga la ïohsngew ba me don kiba khap shñiuh: ki nongaplangbrot jong me ki la don bad ngi, te ngim shym lehbeiñ ïa ki, bad baroh kita ki sngi ba ki la don ha Karmel, kim shym la jah ei ei ruh em.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> To kylli ïa la ki samla, te kin ïathuh ïa me: namar kata, to ai ba kine ki samla kin shem ka jingsngewbha ha khmat jong me; namar ngi la wan, ha ka sngi ka babha: to ai, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa kaei kaei kaba ha ka kti jong me, ha ki shakri jong me, bad ha u Dabid u khun jong me.’ ”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba kita ki samla u Dabid ki la poi, ki la ïathuh ha u Nabal katba kum kita ki ktien baroh ha ka kyrteng u Dabid, bad ki la sngap jar.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Nabal u la ïathuh ha kita ki shakri u Dabid, bad u la ong, “U Dabid u long uei? Bad uei u khun u Jesse? don bun ki shakri ha kine ki sngi kiba phet noh uwei pa uwei na la u kynrad.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ngan shim ïa la u kpu, bad ïa la ka um, bad ïa la ka doh ïa kaba nga la shohdoh ïa la ki nongkhap shñiuh, bad ai ïa ki ha ki briew ïa kiba ngam tip ki nangno?”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Kumta, kita ki samla u Dabid ki la phai noh, bad ki la leit wan noh, bad ki la poi bad ki la ïathuh ha u ïa kita ki ktien baroh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ïa la u paidbah, “To kieng uwei pa uwei ïa la ka waitlam.” Bad ki la kieng uwei pa uwei baroh ïa la ka waitlam; bad u Dabid ruh u la kieng ïa la ka waitlam: te ki la leit kiew kumba sawspah ki briew hadien u Dabid; bad arspah ngut ki la sah bad ki jingbuh jingsat.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te uwei na kita ki samla u la ïathuh ha ka Abigail, ka tnga u Nabal, u da ong, “Ha khmih, u Dabid u la phah ïa ki nongkit-ktien na ka ri khlaw ban khublei ïa u kynrad jong ngi; hynrei, u la krenbeiñ sat ïa ki:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> hynrei, kita ki briew ki la leh bha shibun ïa ngi; bad ym shym la lehbeiñ ïa ngi, lymne ym shym jah ei ei ka jong ngi katba ngi la ïashong hajan jong ki, mynba ngi la don ha lyngkha:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ki la long kum ka kynroh ker ïa ngi mynmiet bad mynsngi, baroh kita ki sngi ba ngi la don lem bad ki ba ngi da sumar ïa ki langbrot.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Mynta te namar kata, to tip bad to pyrkhat ïa kaei ba phan sa leh; namar la thew ïa ka basniew ïa u kynrad jong ngi, bad ka ïing jong u baroh: naba u long u khun u Belial katta katta, katba ym lah ïakren shuh bad u.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ynda kumta, ka Abigail ka la pynkloi bad ka la shim arspah tylli ki kpu, bad ka Waiñ ar lywa, bad san tylli ki langbrot ba la khreh lypa, bad san shang u Kew ba la sdieh, bad shispah rynjup ki soh kismis, bad arspah tylli ki kpu stang u soh Dumbur, bad ka la buh ïa ki halor ki kadda.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ka la ong ha la ki shakri, “To leit ma phi ha shuwa jong nga; ha khmih, ngan sa wan hadien jong phi:” hynrei, kam shym ïathuh ïa la u tnga u Nabal.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te katba ka shong halor ka kadda, bad ba ka dang hiar na ka ranab uta u lum, te, ha khmih u Dabid bad u paid jong u ki ïawan hiar pyrshah ïa ka; bad ka la ïashem bad ki.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Dabid u la lah ong, “Shisha lehnohei ba nga la da ïa kiei kiei baroh ba une u don ha ka ri khlaw, katba ym shym la jah noh ei ei ruh em na kita baroh ki jong u; bad u la siew kylliang ïa nga da ka basniew namar ka babha.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> To U Blei un leh kumta bad tam ruh ïa ki nongshun u Dabid, lada ngan pynsah im na kiei kiei baroh ki jong u hamar ba ka la shai mynstep ïa uwei ruh u khun shynrang.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba ka Abigail ka la ïohi ïa u Dabid, ka la pynkloi bad ka la hiar na kata ka kadda, bad ka la hap dem la ka khmat ha khmat u Dabid, bad ka la dem ngon haduh khyndew.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ka la hap ha ki kjat jong u, bad ka la ong, “Ko kynrad jong nga, to kane ka pop kan long halor jong nga, halor jong nga hi keiñ: nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa ka shakri jong me ba kan kren ha me, to shahshkor ruh ïa ki ktien ka shakri jong me.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nga kyrpad, wat ai ba u kynrad jong nga un ñiew ei ei ïa une u riew Belial, une u Nabal keiñ: naba kumba long ka kyrteng jong u, kumta ruh u long ma u; ‘u Nabal’ long ka kyrteng jong u, bad ka jingbieit ka snoh ha u: hynrei, ma nga ka shakri jong me ngam shym ïohi ïa kita ki shakri u kynrad jong nga, kiba me la phah.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Mynta te, ko kynrad jong nga, katba im U Trai, bad katba im ka mynsiem jong me, namar ba U Trai u la khang ïa me ban ym pynmih snam, bad ban ym pynhiar kput da la ka jong ka kti, to ai te ïa ki nongshun jong me, bad kita kiba thew ïa ka basniew ïa u kynrad jong nga, ba kin long kum une u Nabal.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te mynta kane ka jingai sngewbha kaba ka shakri jong me ka la wallam ïa u kynrad jong nga, to kan long ka jong kine ki samla kiba bud ïa u kynrad jong nga.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> To map, nga kyrpad ïa me, ïa ka jingpalat ka shakri jong me: namar U Trai da shisha un pynlong ka ïing kaba skhem ïa u kynrad jong nga, naba u kynrad jong nga u ïaleh ïa ki jingïaleh thma ki jong U Trai; bad yn ym shem ei ei ka basniew ha me baroh ki sngi jong me.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> La u briew u la ïeng ïa ka ban beh ïa me ruh, bad ban wad ïa ka mynsiem jong me, pynban, ka mynsiem u kynrad jong nga kan long ba la tehsong ha ka jingteh ka jingim bad U Trai U Blei jong me; bad ïa ki mynsiem ki nongshun jong me un shat noh, kum na ka pdeng ka jingshat maw.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te haba U Trai un leh ïa u kynrad jong nga katba kum kita kiei kiei baroh ki babha ïa kiba u la kren shaphang jong me, bad ba un thung nongsynshar ïa me halor ki Israel;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> te kane kan ym long ka jingkhuslai ïa me, lymne ka jingpang dohnud ïa u kynrad jong nga, ba me la pynmih snam khlem daw, lymne ba u kynrad jong nga u la pynhiar kput ma u hi: te haba U Trai u la leh ïa ka babha ïa u kynrad jong nga, ynda kumta, to kynmaw ïa la ka shakri.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha ka Abigail, “Long ba la kyrkhu ïa U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, uba la phah ïa pha ha kane ka sngi ban ïashem bad nga:",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> bad to long ba la kyrkhu ïa ka jingleh stad jong pha, bad to long ba la kyrkhu ma pha ruh, kaba la khang ïa nga ha kane ka sngi ba ngan ym pynmih snam, bad ban ym pynhiar kput da la ka jong ka kti.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Namar da shisha, katba im U Trai, U Blei ki Israel, uba la khang ïa nga ba ngan ym pynsniew ïa pha, lymda pha la pynkloi ma pha ïa ka ban wan ïashem bad nga, shisha yn ym da la pynsah ïa u Nabal hamar kaba lashai mynstep uwei ruh u khun shynrang.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la pdiang na ka kti jong ka ïa kita kiei kiei kiba ka la wallam ha u: bad u la ong ha ka, “To khie leit kiew ha kaba suk sha la ïing; ha khmih, nga la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong pha, bad nga la pdiang sngewbha ïa pha.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te ka Abigail ka la wan sha u Nabal; te, ha khmih, u don ka jingkhawai ha la ïing, kum ka jingkhawai syiem; bad ka dohnud u Nabal ka la kmen eh hapoh jong u, naba u la buaid eh: namar kata, kam shym ïathuh shikyntien ruh ha u, lymne ka barit lymne ka bakhraw, haduh ba kan da shai mynstep.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te mynstep, haba kata ka jingbuaid u Nabal ka la pyngngad, te ka tnga jong u ka la ïathuh ha u ïa kine ki ktien, te ka dohnud jong u ka la ïap noh hapoh jong u, bad u la kylla long kum u maw.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bad ynda la dep kumba shiphew sngi, U Trai u la shoh ïa u Nabal, ba kumta u la ïap noh.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te haba u Dabid u la ïohsngew ba la ïap u Nabal, u la ong, “Long ba la kyrkhu U Trai, uba la ïasaid ïa ka daw ka jingjahburom jong nga na ka kti u Nabal, bad uba la khang ïa la u shakri na kaba leh sniew: naba U Trai u la pynphai ïa ka jinglehsniew u Nabal halor ka khlieh jong u hi.” Bad u Dabid u la phah ïakren bad ka Abigail, ïa ka ban shim kurim ïa ka.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad haba ki shakri u Dabid ki la wan poi sha ka Abigail sha Karmel, ki la ïakren ha ka, ki da ong, “U Dabid u la phah ïa ngi sha pha, ïa ka ban shim kurim ïa pha ha u.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te ka la ïeng, bad ka la dem ngon haduh khyndew, bad ka la ong, “Ha khmih, ka shakri jong me kan long ka shakri ïa ka ban sait ïa ki sla'jat ki shakri u kynrad jong nga.”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad ka Abigail ka la pynkloi, bad ka la ïeng bad ka la shong halor ka kadda, bad san ngut na ki samla kynthei jong ka ki la bud ïa ka; te ka la leit bud ïa kita ki nongkit-ktien u Dabid, bad ka la long ka tnga jong u.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shim ruh ïa ka Ahinoam na Jesril; te kine baroh ar ngut ki la long ki tnga jong u.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Hynrei, u Saul u la lah ai ïa ka Mikhal ka khun jong u, kaba ka tnga u Dabid, ha u Phalti u khun u Laish, uba na Gallim."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki Siph ki la wan sha u Saul ha Gibeah, ki ïa-ong, “U Dabid um buhrieh ïa lade ha i lum Hakhilah, ha marpyrshah ka Jeshimon?”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ynda kumta, u Saul u la ïeng, bad u la leit hiar sha ka ri khlaw Siph, u da don lem bad u lai hajar ki rangbah ba la kynsai na ki Israel, ïa ka ban wad ïa u Dabid ha ka ri khlaw Siph.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Saul u la shong dara ha ita i lum Hakhilah, iba ha marpyrshah ka Jeshimon, hajan ka lynti. Hynrei, u Dabid u la shong ha kata ka ri khlaw, bad u la ïohi ïa u Saul ba u wan wad ïa u sha ka ri khlaw.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Namar kata, u Dabid u la phah ïa ki nongsyntiat, bad u la ïoh tip ba u Saul u la wan shisha.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Dabid u la ïeng, bad u la wan poi sha kata ka jaka ha kaba u Saul u shong dara: bad u Dabid u la ïohi ïa ka jaka ha kaba u Saul u la thiah, bad u Abner u khun u Ner, u nongïalam u paidïapom jong u: te u Saul u la thiah hapdeng ka jaka shong dara, bad u paidbah u shong dara baroh sawdong ïa u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la kren bad u ong ha u Ahimelekh uba kynja Hit, bad ha u Abishai u khun ka Seruïah, u para u Joab, u da ong, “Uei u ban leit hiar bad nga sha u Saul ha kata ka jaka shong dara?” Te u Abishai u la ïathuh, “Ngan leit hiar ma nga bad me.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Kumta, u Dabid bad u Abishai ki la wan poi sha uta u paidbah mynmiet: te, ha khmih, u Saul u thiah ba u da ïohthiah ha kata ka jaka shong dara, bad u sum jong u ba la sieh ha ka khyndew hajan ka syngkhlieh jong u: bad u Abner bad uta u paidbah ki thiah baroh sawdong ïa u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, u Abishai u la ong ha u Dabid, “U Blei ha kane ka sngi u la aiti ïa u nongshun jong me ha ka kti jong me: mynta te namar kata, to shah ïa nga, nga kyrpad ïa me, ba ngan sum syndon ïa u da une u sum haduh khyndew, te ngan ym sum ar sien ïa u.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ïa u Abishai, “Wat pynjot ïa u: naba uei ba lah ban rah ïa la ka kti pyrshah ïa uba la sleh jong U Trai khlem kit pop?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Dabid u la ong ruh, “Katba im U Trai, U Trai hi un shoh ïap ïa u; lane kan poi hi ka sngi jong u ïa ka ban ïap; lane un hiar thma, bad un ïap.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> To U Trai un ri kyndong ïa nga ba ngan ym rah ïa la ka kti pyrshah ïa uba la sleh jong U Trai: hynrei, nga kyrpad ïa me, to shim noh mynta ïa uta u sum uba hajan ka syngkhlieh jong u, bad ïa uta u khiew um, bad ngin ïaleit noh.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shim noh ïa uta u sum bad ïa uta u khiew um najan ka syngkhlieh u Saul; bad ki la leit noh, te ym don ba la ïohi, lymne ba la tip, lymne kiba la peit: naba ki la ïohthiah baroh; namar U Trai u la pynïohthiah lyngngai ïa ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la leit sha shiliang, bad u la ïeng halor uwei u lum na jngai: te ki la ïakham jngai shibun:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> te u Dabid u la pyrta ïa uta u paidbah, bad ïa u Abner u khun u Ner, u da ong, “Mem thie balei, Abner?” Ynda kumta, u Abner u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Me uei uba pyrta kumta ha u syiem?”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Abner, “Hato me mem long rangbah? Bad uei uba kat ma me ha Israel? Te balei ba mem shym la sumar ïa la u kynrad u syiem? Naba u la rung uwei na u paidbah ïa ka ban pynïap ïa u syiem u kynrad jong me.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kane kaba me la leh kam long ka babha keiñ. Katba im U Trai, phi ki briew kiba dei hok ban ïap noh, namar ba phim shym la sumar ïa la u kynrad, uba la sleh jong U Trai keiñ. Te mynta, to khmih, hangno uta u sum jong u syiem, bad uta u khiew um uba hajan ka syngkhlieh jong u.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te u Saul u la sngewthuh ïa ka jingsawa u Dabid, bad u la ong, “Kane ka jingsawa jong me, ko Dabid u khun jong nga?” Bad u Dabid u la ïathuh, “Ka long ka jingsawa jong nga, ko syiem kynrad.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> U la ong ruh, “Namar balei ba u kynrad jong nga u beh nadien u shakri jong u? namar ba nga la leh aïu? lane ka basniew aïu ka don ha ka kti jong nga?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata te, nga kyrpad ïa me, ko syiem kynrad jong nga, to sngap ïa ki ktien u shakri jong me. Lada dei U Trai uba la pynkhih ïa me pyrshah ïa nga, to un pdiang ïa ka jingkñia: hynrei, lada ki dei ki khun ki briew, to kin long kiba la tim ha khmat U Trai; namar ki la beh noh ïa nga ha kane ka sngi ba ngam ïoh shongneh ha ka jingïoh kynti U Trai, ki ïa-ong, ‘Khie leit shakri ïa kiwei pat ki blei.’",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te namar kata, wat ai ïa ka snam jong nga ba kan hap ha ka khyndew shawei shawei na khmat U Trai: naba u syiem ki Israel u la wan mih noh ïa ka ban wad ïa u thyllah, kumba uwei u beh ïa ka 'iar khlaw ha ki lum.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ynda kumta, u Saul u la ong, “Nga la leh pop; to wan phai noh, ko Dabid u khun jong nga: namar ngan ym pynsniew shuh ïa me, naba ka jingim jong nga ka la long ka bakordor ha khmat jong me ha kane ka sngi: ha khmih, nga la leh bieit, bad nga la leh bakla shikatdei.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Dabid u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Ha khmih ïa u sum, ko syiem! to un wan sha shiliang uwei na kita ki samla ban shim noh ïa u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te U Trai un ai ïa uwei pa uwei baroh ïa ka hok jong u bad ka jingïaineh jong u: namar U Trai u la aiti noh ïa me ha ka kti jong nga ha kane ka sngi, hynrei, nga ngam treh ban rah ïa la ka kti pyrshah ïa uba la sleh jong U Trai.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te, ha khmih, kumba ka jingim jong me ka la long ka bakordor ha khmat jong nga ha kane ka sngi, kumta to ai ba ka jingim jong nga kan long ka bakordor ha khmat U Trai, bad to ai ba un pyllait ïa nga na ki jingshipa khop baroh.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ynda kumta, u Saul u la ïathuh ha u Dabid, “To long ma me ïa uba la kyrkhu, ko Dabid, u khun jong nga: ma me men ïoh leh ïa ki kam kiba khraw, bad men nang jop nang jop ruh.” Kumta, u Dabid u la leit sha la ka lynti, bad u Saul u la leit phai noh sha la ka jong ka jaka."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha la ka dohnud, “Shisha ha kawei ka sngi yn sa pynjot noh ïa nga da ka kti u Saul: ym don lad kaba kham bha ïa nga ban ïa kaba leit sha ka ri ki Philistia; te u Saul un pyndam shaphang jong nga, bad un ym wad shuh ïa nga ha ki phang Israel baroh: kumta, ngan lait im na ka kti jong u.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ïeng bad u la leit noh, ma u bad kita ki hynriewspah ngut ki rangbah kiba bad u, sha u Akhish u khun u Maokh, u syiem ka Gath.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shong bad u Akhish ha Gath, ma u bad ki rangbah jong u, uwei pa uwei baroh bad la ka ïing, u Dabid bad kita ki ar ngut ki tnga jong u, ka Ahinoam ka nong Jesril, bad ka Abigail, ka tnga u Nabal, ka nong Karmel.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te la ïathuh ha u Saul ba u Dabid u la phet sha Gath: te um shym wad shuh ïa u.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Akhish, “Lada nga la shem kaba sngewbha ha khmat jong me, ai jaka ïa nga ha kawei ka shnong ha ka khyndew jong me, ba ngan ïoh shong hangta: namar u shakri jong me un shong lei bad me ha ka shnong u syiem?”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te kumta, u Akhish u la ai ïa u ha kata hi ka sngi ïa ka Siklag: namar kata, ka Siklag ka long ka jong ki syiem ka Judah haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka jingkheiñ ïa ki sngi ba u Dabid u la shong ha ka ri ki Philistia ka la dap shi snem saw bnai.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Dabid bad ki rangbah jong u ki la mih ïahiar thma ïa ki Geshur, bad ïa ki Geser, bad ïa ki Amalek: namar kita kiba la ju shong mynno mynno ha kata ka ri, shaphang kaba leit sha Shur, jin haduh ka ri Ijipt keiñ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u Dabid u la pom ïa kata ka ri, bad um shym la pynsah im ïa u rangbah lymne ïa ka kynthei, bad u la shim noh ïa ki langbrot, bad ïa ki masi, bad ïa ki kadda, bad ïa ki ut, bad ki jaiñkup jaiñsem; bad u la phai noh, bad u la wan sha u Akhish.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Akhish u la kylli, “Shano phi la hiar thma ha kane ka sngi?” Te u Dabid u la ïathuh, “Pyrshah ïa ka phang shathie ka Judah, bad pyrshah ïa ka phang shathie ki Jerahmil, bad pyrshah ïa ka phang shathie ki Ken.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Dabid um shym la pynsah im ïa u rangbah lymne ïa ka kynthei, ïa ka ban wallam sha Gath, u da ong, “Ïoh ki pynbna ïa ngi da kaba ong, ‘Kumta u la leh u Dabid,’ ” bad kumta ka la long ka rukom jong u katba u nang shong ha ka ri ki Philistia.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad u Akhish u la ngeit ïa u Dabid, u da ong, “U la pyniwkhong ïa lade ha la ki jong ki briew ki Israel; namar kata, un long u shakri jong nga junom.”"
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha kita ki sngi, ki Philistia ki la lum lang ïa la ki paidïapom ïa ka thma, ïa ka ban ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel. Bad u Akhish u la ong ha u Dabid, “To tip skhem, ba men leit mih noh bad nga ha u paidïapom; ma me bad ki rangbah jong me keiñ.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Dabid u la ong ha u Akhish, “Kumta te men ïoh tip keiñ ïa kaba u shakri jong me un leh.” Bad u Akhish u la ong ha u Dabid, “Namar kata, ngan buh ïa me u nongsumar ïa ka khlieh jong nga junom.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te u Samuel u la lah ïap noh, bad ki Israel baroh ki la lah ïambriew ïa u, bad ki la tep ïa u ha Ramah, ha ka shnong jong u hi keiñ. Bad u Saul u la lah beh noh na kata ka ri ïa kiba shong ksuid, bad ïa kiba kren byrtong.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la ïalum khar paid, bad ki la ïawan bad ki la shong dara ha Shunem: bad u Saul u la lum khar paid ïa ki Israel baroh, bad ki la ïashong dara ha Gilboa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba u Saul u la ïohi ïa ka jaka shong dara jong ki Philistia, u la khaw-eit, bad ka dohnud jong u ka la sheptieng shikatdei eh.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Bad haba u la kylli na U Trai, U Trai um shym ïathuh ha u, lymne da ki jingphohsniew, lymne da ki Urim, lymne da ki nongïathuhlypa de.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda kumta, u Saul u la ong ha la ki shakri, “To wad keiñ ha nga da ka kynthei kaba shong ksuid, ba ngan ïoh leit sha ka, bad ba ngan kylli na ka.” Bad kita ki shakri jong u ki la ïathuh ha u, “Ha khmih, ka don kawei ka kynthei kaba shong ksuid ha Endor.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Saul u la pynpher ïa lade, bad u la kup da kiwei pat ki jaiñ, bad u la leit, ma u bad ar ngut ki rangbah lem bad u, bad ki la poi sha kata ka kynthei mynmiet. Bad u la ong ha ka, “Nga kyrpad ïa pha, to kylli ksuid ïa nga, bad to pynmih ha nga ïa uta uba ngan ïathuh ha pha.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te kata ka kynthei ka la ïathuh ha u, “Ha khmih, me tip ïa kaba u la leh u Saul, uba la pynduh noh na kane ka ri ïa kiba shong ksuid, bad ïa kiba kren byrtong: namar kata, balei ba me buh ïa ka jingriam ïa ka jingim jong nga, ïa ka ban pynïap ïa nga?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u Saul u la smai ha ka ha U Trai, u da ong, “Katba im U Trai, kan ym jia ei ei ka jingpynshitom ïa pha namar kane ka kam.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, kata ka kynthei ka la kylli ïa u, “Ïano ngan pynmih ha me?” U te u la ïathuh, “To pynmih ha nga ïa u Samuel.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad haba kata ka kynthei ka la ïohi ïa u Samuel, ka la lynñiar da ka ktien kaba jam: bad kata ka kynthei ka la kren ha u Saul, ka da ong, “Balei me la shukor ïa nga? Naba me long u Saul hi.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u syiem u la ong ha ka, “Wat sheptieng: namar pha ïohi aïu?” Bad kata ka kynthei ka la ïathuh ha u Saul, “Nga la ïohi ki blei ba ki mih na ka khyndew.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U ruh u la kylli ïa ka, “Ka dur kaba kumno u don?” Te ka la ïathuh, “U kynja riewtymmen u mih artet; bad u kup da ka barandi.” Te u Saul u la tip ba u long u Samuel, bad u la dem ngon haduh khyndew, bad u la nguh.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Samuel u la ong ha u Saul, “Balei ba me la pynkhih ïa nga, ïa ka ban pynmih ïa nga?” Te u Saul u la ïathuh, “Ma nga, nga la shipa noh khop; namar ki Philistia ki ïaleh thma ïa nga, bad U Blei u la kynriah noh na nga, bad um ïathuh shuh ïa nga, lymne da ki nongïathuhlypa, lymne da ki jingphohsniew; namar kata, nga la khot ïa me, ba men pyntip ïa nga ïa kaei kaba nga dei ban leh.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, u Samuel u la ong, “Na ka balei te ba me ïakylli na nga, haba U Trai u la kynriah noh na me, bad u la jia long u nongïaleh ïa me?",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Trai shisha u la leh na ka bynta ïa lade, kat kumba u la kren da nga: namar U Trai u la kad noh ïa ka jinglong syiem na ka kti jong me, bad u la aiti ïa ka ha u paramarjan jong me, ha u Dabid keiñ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Namar ba mem shym la shahshkor ma me ïa ka ktien U Trai, bad ba mem shym la pyndep ïa ka jingbitar ba-meh lep jong u halor ki Amalek, namar kata keiñ, ba U Trai u la leh ïa kane ha me ha kane ka sngi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> U Trai un aiti noh ruh ïa ki Israel lem bad me ha ka kti ki Philistia: bad lashai ma me bad kita ki khun shynrang jong me phin ïalong bad nga; U Trai un aiti noh ruh ïa ki paidïapom ki Israel ha ka kti ki Philistia.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hangta te u Saul u la kyllon kynsan kram ha khyndew, bad u la sheptieng shikatdei eh, namar kita ki ktien u Samuel: te um shym don bor shuh ha u; namar um shym la bam jingbam baroh kata ka sngi, bad baroh kata ka miet.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te kata ka kynthei ka la wan sha u Saul, bad ka la ïohi ba u la sngewtriem shikatdei, bad ka la ong ha u, “Ha khmih, ka shakri jong me ka la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong me, bad nga la kheiñduh ïa la ka jingim, bad nga la kohnguh ïa kita ki ktien kiba me la kren ha nga.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Mynta, namar kata, ma me ruh, nga kyrpad ïa me, to shahshkor ïa ka ktien ka shakri jong me, bad to shah ïa nga ban buh ha khmat jong me shikyntien u kpu; bad to bam, ba men ïoh bor ha me, haba me leit sha la ka jingleit.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Hynrei, um treh, bad u la ong, “Ngan ym bam.” Hynrei, ki shakri jong u, bad kata ka kynthei, ki la pynbor ïa u; bad u la shahshkor ïa ka ktien jong ki. Bad u la ïeng na ka khyndew, bad u la shong ha kata ka jingthiah.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te kata ka kynthei ka la don u khun masi basngaid ha ïing; bad ka la pynkloi, bad ka la pynïap ïa u: bad ka la shim ïa u 'purew, bad ka la khleh ïa u, bad ka la shet da uta ïa u kpu bakhlem thiat:",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> bad ka la wallam ha khmat u Saul, bad ha khmat ki shakri jong u; ki te ki la ïabam. Ynda kumta, ki la ïeng, bad ki la leit noh ha kata hi ka miet."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la lum lang ïa ki paidïapom jong ki baroh sha Aphek: bad ki Israel ki la ïashong dara hajan ka pukri kaba ha Jesril.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki nongïalam ki Philistia ki la ïaïaid riang riang shispah shispah bad shi hajar shi hajar: bad u Dabid bad u paid jong u ki la ïaid khatduh lem bad u Akhish.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, kita ki nongïalam ki Philistia ki la ïa-ong, “Kine ki Hebru ki lei hangne!” Te u Akhish u la ïathuh ha kita ki nongïalam ki Philistia, “Une um long u Dabid, u shakri u Saul u syiem ki Israel, uba la don lem bad nga kine ki sngi lane kine ki snem, bad ka pop ei ei ngam shym shem ha u naduh ba u la wanhap ha nga jin haduh kane ka sngi?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kita ki nongïalam ki Philistia ki la bitar lep ïa u; bad kita ki nongïalam ki Philistia ki la ïa-ong ha u, “To pynphai noh ïa une u briew sha kata ka jaka kaba me la buh ïa u, bad wat ai ba un leit hiar bad ngi sha ka thma, ba ïoh un kylla nongïaleh pyrshah ïa ngi ha kata ka thma: namar da ei un pynsngewbha ïa la u kynrad? ym long keiñ da ki khlieh jong kine ki briew?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Balei, une um long uta u Dabid ïa uba ki la ïarwai markylliang ha kita ki jingshad, ki da ïa-ong, “ ‘U Saul u la pynïap ïa la ki hajar, bad u Dabid ïa la ki phew hajar?’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda kumta, u Akhish u la khot ïa u Dabid, bad u la ong ha u, “Katba im U Trai, me la long u bahok, bad ka jingmih shabar jong me bad ka jingwan shapoh jong me lem bad nga ha ka jaka shong dara ka la long kaba sngewbha ha khmat jong nga: namar ngam shym shem ïa ka pop ei ei ha me naduh kata ka sngi kaba me la wan sha nga haduh kane ka sngi: hynrei, kine ki doloi kim sngewbha ïa me.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar kata te, to leit phai pat ha kaba suk, ba men ym pynsngewsih ïa ki doloi ki Philistia.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Dabid u la ïathuh ha u Akhish, “Hato nga la leh aïu ma nga? bad me la shem aïu ha la u shakri katba nga la wan ha khmat jong me haduh kane ka sngi, ba ngam ïoh leit ban ïaleh thma ïa ki nongshun u syiem kynrad jong nga?”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u Akhish u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha u Dabid, “Nga tip keiñ ba me long u babha ha khmat jong nga, kum u angel U Blei keiñ: hynrei, kine ki nongïalam ki Philistia ki la ong, ‘Un ym ïoh leit kiew bad ngi sha kane ka thma.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Namar kata te, to khie la dang step bad kita ki shakri u kynrad jong me kiba la wan lem bad me: bad haba phi la khie dang step, bad ba ka shai, te phin leit noh keiñ.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la khie la dang step, ma u bad uta u paidbah jong u, ïa ka ban leit noh mynstep, ban leit phai pat sha ka ri ki Philistia. Bad ki Philistia ki la leit kiew sha Jesril."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hamar kaba u Dabid bad u paidbah jong u ki la ïawan poi sha Siklag ha ka sngi ka balai, ki Amalek ki la lah hiar thma sha ka phang shathie, bad ha Siklag, bad ki la jop ïa ka Siklag, bad ki la thang ïa ka da ka ding;",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad ki la ring mraw ruh ïa ki kynthei bad baroh kiba ha ka, u barit bad u bakhraw: te kim shym pynïap ïano ïano ruh, hynrei, ki la shu shim noh ïa ki, bad ki la leit noh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba u Dabid bad ki briew jong u ki la poi sha kata ka shnong, ha khmih la lah thang ïa ka da ka ding; bad la ring mraw ïa ki tnga jong ki, bad ïa ki khun shynrang jong ki, bad ïa ki khun kynthei jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid bad uta u paidbah uba bad u, ki la pynjam ïa la ka ktien bad ki la ïam, haduh ba kim don bor shuh ban ïam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> La ring mraw ruh ïa kita ki ar ngut ki tnga u Dabid, ka Ahinoam ka nong Jesril, bad ka Abigail ka tnga u Nabal u nong Karmel.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te u Dabid u la sngewpisa eh; naba kita ki paidbah ki la ïa-ong ban lynthem maw ïa u, namar ki mynsiem jong kita ki briew baroh ki la kthang, uwei pa uwei namar la ki khun shynrang bad namar la ki khun kynthei; hynrei, u Dabid u la pynkhlaiñ ïa lade ha U Trai U Blei jong u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ong ha u Abiathar lyngdoh, u khun u Ahimelekh, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, to wallam shane sha nga ïa kata ka ephod.” Bad u Abiathar u la wallam ïa kata ka ephod ha u Dabid.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Dabid u la kylli na U Trai, u da ong, “Lada ngan beh nadien une u paid, ngan lap ïa u ne em?” U ruh U la ïathuh ha u, “To beh; namar men lap shisha, bad da shisha men ïoh pat ïa kiei kiei baroh.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta, u Dabid u la leit, ma u bad kita ki hynriewspah ngut kiba bad u, bad ki la poi sha ka wah Besor, ha kaba ki la shong kita ïa kiba la iehnoh sah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, u Dabid te u la beh, ma u bad sawspah ngut ki rangbah: naba arspah ngut ki la sah shadien, ba ki la thait eh ba kim lah shuh ban leit shiliang ka wah Besor.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ki la shem ïa uwei u kynja Ijipt ha lum, bad ki la wallam ïa u ha u Dabid, bad ki la ai kpu ïa u ba un bam, bad u la bam; bad ki la ai um dih ruh ïa u:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad ki la ai ha u shi dkhot u 'pu stang soh Dumbur, bad ar rynjup ki soh Kismis; te haba u la lah bam, ka mynsiem jong u ka la wan pat ha u: namar um shym la bam kpu, lymne dih um, la lai sngi bad lai miet.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Dabid u la kylli ïa u, “Ma me u jongno? Bad me uba nangno?” U te u la ïathuh, “Nga u samla uba na ka ri Ijipt, u shakri jong u nong Amalek; te u kynrad jong nga u la iehnoh noh ïa nga, namar ba nga la pang noh mynta la lai sngi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ngi la hiar thma ïa ka shathie jong ki Khereth, bad ïa ka jong ka Judah, bad ïa ka phang shathie jong u Kaleb; bad ïa ka Siklag ngi la thang da ka ding.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te u Dabid u la kylli ïa u, “Me lah ban ïalam arsut ïa nga sha une u paid?” U ruh u la ïathuh, “To smai ha nga ha U Blei, ba men ym pynïap ïa nga, lymne aiti noh ïa nga ha ka kti uta u kynrad jong nga, bad nga ruh ngan ïalam arsut ïa me sha une u paid.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te haba u la ïalam arsut ïa u, ha khmih, ki la phriang ïa lade ha kata ka jaka baroh, ki da bam, bad ki da dih, bad ki da khawai de, namar kata ka jinglute kaba khraw baroh ïa kaba ki la shim na ri ki Philistia, bad na ka ri Judah.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Bad u Dabid u la pom noh ïa ki naduh janmiet haduh kaba la noh ka sngi lashai; te ym shym la lait noh uwei na ki, hynrei, tang sawspah ngut ki samla, kiba la shong halor ki ut bad ki la phet ïap noh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad u Dabid u la ïoh pat ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba ki la lah shim ki Amalek: bad u Dabid u la pynim pat ïa la ki tnga baroh ar ngut.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te kim shym la duna ei ei ruh, lymne ka barit lymne ka bakhraw, lymne u khun shynrang lymne ka khun kynthei, lymne ka jinglute, lymne kaei kaei ruh na kita kiba ki la shim noh: u Dabid u la wallam pat ïa kiei kiei baroh.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bad u Dabid u la shim noh ruh ïa ki langbrot baroh bad ïa ki masi, ïa kiba ki la ñiah ha shuwa kita kiwei ki jingri, bad ki la ïa-ong, “Kane ka jinglute u Dabid.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te u Dabid u la wan poi sha kita ki arspah ngut ki rangbah, kiba la thait eh ba kumta te kim lah shuh ban bud ïa u Dabid, bad ba la pynsah ïa ki ha kata ka wah Besor: ki ruh ki la ïamih ban leit tan ïa u Dabid, bad ban tan ïa uta u paidbah uba la don lem bad u: bad haba u Dabid u la wan hajan uta u paidbah, u la khublei ïa ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, kita ki riewbymman baroh bad kita ki riew Belial na kita kiba la leit lem bad u Dabid, ki la ïathuh bad ki la ïa-ong, “Namar ba kine kim shym leit lem bad ngi, ngi ruh ngin ym ai ha ki na kane ka jinglute ïa kaba ngi la ïoh pat, hynrei, ïa uwei pa uwei tang ïa la ka tnga bad ki khun, ba kin shim noh ïa kita, bad kin leit noh keiñ.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ynda kumta, u Dabid u la ong, “Ko ki para jong nga, phin ym leh kumta ïa kata kaba u la ai U Trai ha ngi, uba la sumar ïa ngi, bad uba la aiti noh ha ka kti jong ngi ïa uta u paidbah uba la wan ïaleh ïa ngi.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad uei u ban shahshkor ïa phi ha kane ka kam? naba kumba long ka bynta jong uta uba leit hiar ha ka thma, kumta hi keiñ kan long ka bynta jong uta uba sah bad ki jingbuh jingsat; kin ïasam mar kumjuh keiñ.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te naduh kata ka sngi, u la buh ïa kane ban long ka aiñ bad ka rukom ha Israel, haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad haba u Dabid u la poi sha Siklag, u la phah ai na kata ka jinglute ha ki tymmen basan ka Judah, kata, ha kita ki lok jong u, u da ong, “Ha khmih kane ka jingai sngewbha ha phi na ka jinglute ki nongshun U Trai;”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ha kiba ha Bethel, bad ha kiba ha Ramoth kaba shaphang shathie, bad ha kiba ha Jattir;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> bad ha kiba ha Aroer, bad ha kiba ha Siphmoth, bad ha kiba ha Eshtemoa;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> bad ha kiba ha Rakhal, bad ha kiba ha ki nongbah ki Jerahmil, bad ha kiba ha ki nongbah ki Ken;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad ha kiba ha Hormah, bad ha kiba ha Khorashan, bad ha kiba ha Athak;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad ha kiba ha Hebron, bad ha kita ki jaka baroh ha kiba u Dabid bad u paidbah jong u ki la ju shong ha ki."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki Philistia ki la ïaleh thma ïa ki Israel: bad ki paidïapom ki Israel ki la phet ïap noh ha khmat ki Philistia, bad ki la kyllon ba la pynïap ïa ki ha u lum Gilboa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki Philistia ki la beh eh ïa u Saul bad ki khun shynrang jong u; bad ki Philistia ki la pynïap ïa u Jonathan, bad ïa u Abinadab, bad ïa u Melkhi-shua, ki khun u Saul.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ka thma ka la nang jur nang jur halor u Saul, bad ki nongsiat khnam ki la lap ïa u; bad u la pisa eh namar kita kiba siat khnam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u Saul u la ong ha uta uba rah ïa ki atiar jong u, “To sei ïa la ka waitlam, bad to dung peib'la ïa nga da ka; ïoh kine ïa ki bym shym la otsher kin wan bad dung peib'la ïa nga, bad ba kin lehbeiñ ïa nga.” Hynrei, uta u nongrah atiar jong u um treh, namar ba u la sheptieng eh. Namar kata, u Saul u la shim ïa la ka waitlam, bad u la hap halor jong ka.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad haba uta u nongrah atiar jong u, u la ïohi ba u la ïap u Saul, u ruh u la hap ha la ka waitlam, bad u la ïap lem bad u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, u Saul, bad kita ki khun shynrang jong u, bad uta u nongrah atiar jong u, bad ki rangbah jong u baroh, ki la ïaïap-lem bad u ha kata ka sngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba kita ki rangbah Israel kiba sha shiliang kata ka them, bad kita kiba sha shiliang ka Jordan, ki la ïohi ba kita ki paidïapom ki Israel ki la phet ïap, bad ba la ïap u Saul bad ki khun jong u, ki ruh ki la iehnoh noh ïa la ki shnong, bad ki la phet ïap noh; bad ki Philistia ki la ïawan bad ki la shong shnong ha ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mynstep te, haba ki Philistia ki la wan ïa ka ban loit jaiñ ïa kita ïa kiba la pynïap, ki la shem keiñ ïa u Saul bad ïa kita ki khun shynrang jong u lai ngut ba la kyllon ha u lum Gilboa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ki la khrai ïa ka khlieh jong u, bad ki la loit noh ïa ki atiar jong u, bad ki la phah sha ka ri ki Philistia baroh kylleng, ïa ka ban pynbna ïa kata ha ki ïing ki bleithaw jong ki, bad ha ki paidbah.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad ki la buh ïa ki atiar jong u ha ka ïing ki Ashtaroth: te ïa ka met jong u ki la sahnar ha ka kynroh ka Beth-shan.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba ki nong Jabesh-gilead ki la ïohsngew shaphang jong u ïa kaba ki la leh ki Philistia ha u Saul,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ki rangbah badonbor baroh ki la ïaïeng, bad ki la ïaid baroh shi miet, bad ki la shim noh ïa ka met u Saul bad ïa ki met ki khun jong u na kata ka kynroh ka Beth-shan; bad haba ki la wan poi sha Jabesh, ki la thang ïa ki hangta.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ki la shim ïa ki shyieng jong ki, bad ki la tep ïa ki hapoh uwei u dieng ha Jabesh, bad ki la ïashah jingit hynñiew sngi."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;